Dialogue: 100,0:00:34.77,0:00:36.10,UNNM_Main_1080p,Ao,0,0,0,,{Đã lâu rồi nhỉ. - It's been a while, hasn't it?}Cũng lâu rồi...
Dialogue: 100,0:00:37.06,0:00:38.69,UNNM_Main_1080p,Ao,0,0,0,,{Hẹn gặp kiểu ba người như thế này ấy. - Since we've all been together.}cả ba mới hẹn gặp như vầy ha.
Dialogue: 100,0:00:38.98,0:00:40.10,UNNM_Main_1080p,To,0,0,0,,{Cũng phải. - It really has.}Ừm.
Dialogue: 100,0:00:41.02,0:00:42.06,UNNM_Main_1080p,To,0,0,0,,{Xin lỗi vì tôi đến muộn. - Sorry we couldn't do this sooner.}Xin lỗi vì tới giờ mới hẹn gặp được.
Dialogue: 100,0:00:42.31,0:00:43.48,UNNM_Main_1080p,Ry,0,0,0,,{Đừng để ý làm gì. - Don't worry about it.}Có gì đâu mà xin lỗi.
Dialogue: 100,0:00:44.19,0:00:45.86,UNNM_Main_1080p,Ry,0,0,0,,{Được gặp hai người thôi tôi cũng thấy vui rồi. - I'm just glad we can see each other at all.}Được gặp là đã vui lắm rồi.
Dialogue: 100,0:00:49.36,0:00:52.37,UNNM_Main_1080p,To,0,0,0,,{Mùa hè, lại đến rồi nhỉ. - So, summer's come again, huh?}Lại tới mùa hè rồi ha?
Dialogue: 100,0:00:56.91,0:00:58.71,UNNM_Main_1080p,Ry,0,0,0,,{Đã một năm trôi qua rồi hả. - A year's come and gone, huh?}Vậy là qua một năm rồi à.
Dialogue: 100,0:01:01.59,0:01:02.71,UNNM_Main_1080p,To,0,0,0,,Ayane.{Ayane.}
Dialogue: 100,0:01:20.10,0:01:21.19,UNNM_Main_1080p,To,0,0,0,,Bạn là Aoi phải không?{Are you Aoi?}
Dialogue: 100,0:01:21.19,0:01:23.23,UNNM_Main_1080p,Ao,0,0,0,,{Vâng. - Ah, yeah.}A, ừm.
Dialogue: 100,0:01:23.23,0:01:26.40,UNNM_Main_1080p,To,0,0,0,,{Lần đầu gặp mặt, tôi là Sugisaki Tomoya. - Cool. I'm Sugisaki Tomoya.}Chào bạn nha. Mình là Sugisaki Tomoya.
Dialogue: 100,0:01:26.86,0:01:27.73,UNNM_Main_1080p,To,0,0,0,,{Hân hạnh được làm quen. - Nice to meet you.}Xin được làm quen.
Dialogue: 100,0:01:28.53,0:01:29.65,UNNM_Main_1080p,Ry,0,0,0,,Rốp rẻng vậy.{You guys are eager.}
Dialogue: 100,0:01:31.07,0:01:32.45,UNNM_Main_1080p,Ry,0,0,0,,{Vẫn còn 5 phút nữa đó. - Even I've got five minutes.}5 phút nữa mới tới giờ mà.
Dialogue: 100,0:01:33.95,0:01:34.99,UNNM_Main_1080p,Ry,0,0,0,,Tôi là Ryou.{I'm Ryou.}
Dialogue: 100,0:01:35.45,0:01:36.41,UNNM_Main_1080p,Ry,0,0,0,,Hân hạnh được làm quen.{Nice to meet you two.}
Dialogue: 100,0:01:36.41,0:01:37.54,UNNM_Main_1080p,Ao,0,0,0,,{Rất hân hạnh. - You, too.}Ừm, chào bạn nha.
Dialogue: 100,0:01:37.54,0:01:39.91,UNNM_Main_1080p,To,0,0,0,,Coi bộ đông đủ rồi.{Okay. Looks like we're all here.}
Dialogue: 100,0:01:41.62,0:01:43.13,UNNM_Main_1080p,To,0,0,0,,{Vậy thì, bắt đầu thôi nào. - Shall we get started?}Bắt tay vào việc thôi.
Dialogue: 100,0:01:47.17,0:01:48.30,UNNM_Main_1080p,To,0,0,0,,Trước tiên phải kiểm tra cái đã.{First, let's lay everything out.}
Dialogue: 100,0:01:48.67,0:01:52.51,UNNM_Main_1080p,To,0,0,0,,{Lý do chúng ta tập trung ở đây là để đi tìm hồn ma. - We all came here today to find a ghost.}Bữa nay ba đứa tới đây là để tìm một hồn ma.
Dialogue: 100,0:01:52.76,0:01:54.09,UNNM_Main_1080p,To,0,0,0,,{Tên thường gọi là "Summer Ghost". - The Summer Ghost, to be exact.}Phải gọi là Bóng Ma Mùa Hạ mới đúng.
Dialogue: 100,0:01:54.55,0:01:55.72,UNNM_Main_1080p,To,0,0,0,,Từ khoảng mấy năm trước,{For the past couple years,}
Dialogue: 100,0:01:56.35,0:01:58.10,UNNM_Main_1080p,To,0,0,0,,{chỉ đúng chỗ này vào mùa hè\Nmới có người chứng kiến. - it's been spotted around here every summer.}người ta hay thấy nó loanh quanh khu này nè.
Dialogue: 100,0:01:58.60,0:02:00.68,UNNM_Main_1080p,Ry,0,0,0,,{Có lời đồn nếu đốt pháo hoa thì nó sẽ ra đó. - I hear you've gotta have fireworks.}Nghe đồn đốt pháo hoa là nó chui ra á.
Dialogue: 100,0:02:01.10,0:02:01.98,UNNM_Main_1080p,Ao,0,0,0,,Pháo hoa?{Fireworks?}
Dialogue: 100,0:02:01.98,0:02:04.56,UNNM_Main_1080p,Ry,0,0,0,,{[/q2]Ừ, những người mà thấy tất cả đều đốt cả. - Yeah. Apparently everyone \Nwho's seen it was playing with 'em.}Ừ. Hình như người nào thấy đều có đốt hết.
Dialogue: 100,0:02:06.27,0:02:07.90,UNNM_Main_1080p,To,0,0,0,,Ngoại hình là một cô gái trên dưới 20 tuổi.{It's supposedly a woman \Nin her early twenties.}
Dialogue: 100,0:02:09.15,0:02:11.70,UNNM_Main_1080p,To,0,0,0,,Tóc dài, mặc quần áo đen.{She's got long hair and black clothes.}
Dialogue: 100,0:02:12.61,0:02:15.53,UNNM_Main_1080p,To,0,0,0,,{\q2}Nếu mà cần minh hoạ thì chắc sẽ giống vầy.{If I had to draw her, \Nshe'd probably look something like this.}
Dialogue: 100,0:02:15.91,0:02:16.95,UNNM_Main_1080p,Ao,0,0,0,,{Giỏi vậy. - You're so good.}Đẹp vậy.
Dialogue: 100,0:02:18.49,0:02:20.12,UNNM_Main_1080p,Ry,0,0,0,,Người đẹp như thế này á hả?{A pretty lady like her, huh?}
Dialogue: 100,0:02:21.96,0:02:23.67,UNNM_Main_1080p,To,0,0,0,,{Nếu theo lời đồn thì hồn ma này, - If the rumors are true, then this ghost}Nếu người ta đồn đúng, thì đây là hồn ma
Dialogue: 100,0:02:25.54,0:02:27.42,UNNM_Main_1080p,To,0,0,0,,{là hồn ma của người đã tự sát. - is the ghost of someone \Nwho committed suicide.}của người đã tự vẫn.
Dialogue: 100,0:02:32.38,0:02:33.18,UNNM_Main_1080p,To,0,0,0,,Sao vậy?{What's wrong?}
Dialogue: 100,0:02:33.18,0:02:34.80,UNNM_Main_1080p,Ao,0,0,0,,H-Hổng có gì.{O-Oh, it's nothing.}
Dialogue: 100,0:02:35.43,0:02:39.26,UNNM_Main_1080p,Ao,0,0,0,,{[/q2]bình tĩnh lại rồi thì tôi thấy hơi sợ ma một chút. - Just, now that it's had time to sink in, \NI've realized I'm kinda scared of ghosts.}Chẳng qua là giờ suy nghĩ thấu đáo rồi\Nmới nhớ ra mình hơi sợ ma.
Dialogue: 100,0:02:39.26,0:02:41.06,UNNM_Main_1080p,Ry,0,0,0,,{Mãi đến giờ á? - This late in the game?}{Giờ mới nhớ hả? - OG}Đi tới đây rồi mới nhớ hả?
Dialogue: 100,0:02:42.14,0:02:43.89,UNNM_Main_1080p,Ry,0,0,0,,{Mà, quay đầu về cũng được. - I mean, whatever, you don't have to come.}Thôi, sợ thì cứ về đi.
Dialogue: 100,0:02:43.89,0:02:44.52,UNNM_Main_1080p,Ry,0,0,0,,Thằng này vẫn đi.{I know I'm going.}
Dialogue: 100,0:02:44.52,0:02:48.27,UNNM_Main_1080p,Ao,0,0,0,,{Xin lỗi xin lỗi, tôi cũng sẽ đi mà. - Sorry! I'm just being silly! I'm coming, too!}Xin lỗi mà! Coi như chưa nói gì đi! \NĐể mình đi chung nữa!
Dialogue: 100,0:02:48.27,0:02:50.82,UNNM_Main_1080p,Ao,0,0,0,,{Nói là sợ nhưng cũng chỉ có tẹo thôi mà. - Sure, I'm scared, but it's just a little bit.}Có sợ thiệt, nhưng mà có chút xíu à.
Dialogue: 100,0:02:50.82,0:02:55.45,UNNM_Main_1080p,Ao,0,0,0,,{[/q2]Vậy thì xem nào, tại sao Tomoya\Nlại muốn đi gặp hồn ma hả? - Oh, actually, why do you want \Nto see this ghost, Tomoya?}Mà cho hỏi cái nha, sao Tomoya \Nlại muốn gặp hồn ma này dạ?
Dialogue: 100,0:02:55.45,0:02:58.24,UNNM_Main_1080p,Ao,0,0,0,,{\q2}{[/q2]Người đã gửi thư cho chúng tôi\Nlà Tomoya phải không? - I mean, you were the one \Nwho reached out to us about this.}Tại bạn là người liên lạc với tụi mình mà phải hông nè?
Dialogue: 100,0:02:59.99,0:03:00.70,UNNM_Main_1080p,To,0,0,0,,{Bí mật. - Who knows?}Không nói đâu.
Dialogue: 100,0:03:00.95,0:03:03.29,UNNM_Main_1080p,Ao,0,0,0,,{Ủa, tại sao? - Come on! What's that about?}Ủa? Kỳ cục vậy!
Dialogue: 100,0:03:03.79,0:03:04.46,UNNM_Main_1080p,Ry,0,0,0,,Lạnh lùng ghê.{Ouch, dude.}
Dialogue: 100,0:03:09.29,0:03:10.75,UNNM_Main_1080p,Te,0,0,0,,Sugisaki.{Sugisaki.}
Dialogue: 100,0:03:11.63,0:03:15.26,UNNM_Main_1080p,Te,0,0,0,,A, A, A, A, A...
Dialogue: 100,0:03:16.05,0:03:17.68,UNNM_Main_1080p,Te,0,0,0,,Không có gì để chê.{Looking good.}
Dialogue: 100,0:03:17.68,0:03:20.22,UNNM_Main_1080p,Te,0,0,0,,{Em vẫn như mọi khi nhỉ. - You never fail to impress me.}Vẫn giỏi như bao ngày.
Dialogue: 100,0:03:20.22,0:03:22.51,UNNM_Main_1080p,Te,0,0,0,,{Thấy cũng muốn mấy đứa khác học hỏi theo lắm. - I wish the other students \Nwould learn from you.}Phải chi mấy đứa khác lấy em làm gương thì tốt.
Dialogue: 100,0:03:22.94,0:03:24.22,UNNM_Main_1080p,To,0,0,0,,{Cảm ơn thầy rất nhiều. - Thank you.}Cảm ơn thầy đã khen.
Dialogue: 100,0:03:25.64,0:03:26.98,UNNM_Main_1080p,Te,0,0,0,,Sugisaki.{Sugisaki.}
Dialogue: 100,0:03:26.98,0:03:27.75,UNNM_Main_1080p,To,0,0,0,,{Vâng. - Yes, sir?}Dạ?
Dialogue: 100,0:03:30.65,0:03:31.69,UNNM_Main_1080p,Te,0,0,0,check,{Thầy kỳ vọng vào em. - You're gonna go far.}Tương lai em xán lạn đó.
Dialogue: 100,0:03:54.97,0:03:55.42,UNNM_Main_1080p,Ry,0,0,0,,Tomoya.{Tomoya.}
Dialogue: 100,0:03:57.93,0:03:59.51,UNNM_Main_1080p,Ry,0,0,0,,{Có chuyện gì sao mà khuôn mặt như vậy. - What are you spacing out for?}Bị gì mà đứng đực ra vậy?
Dialogue: 100,0:04:00.68,0:04:01.51,UNNM_Main_1080p,Ry,0,0,0,,{Đến rồi đó. - We're here.}Tới rồi.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:13.90,0:04:14.99,UNNM_Main_1080p,Ao,0,0,0,,{Rộng ghê. - Look at all this space!}Rộng quá trời ha!
Dialogue: 100,0:04:14.99,0:04:17.07,UNNM_Main_1080p,To,0,0,0,,Ngày xưa đây là sân bay đấy.{This used to be an airport.}
Dialogue: 100,0:04:17.07,0:04:19.07,UNNM_Main_1080p,To,0,0,0,,Hình như làm ăn không thuận lợi nên mới đóng cửa.{I heard it closed down \Nbecause it wasn't profitable.}
Dialogue: 100,0:04:19.07,0:04:21.74,UNNM_Main_1080p,Ry,0,0,0,,{Này. Mau làm nhanh đê. - Guys! Let's get started already.}Hai đứa kia! Khẩn trương lên.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:28.21,0:04:31.34,UNNM_Main_1080p,Ao,0,0,0,,{Thực sự là có không nhỉ, Summer Ghost ấy. - You think this Summer Ghost really exists?}Rồi hổng biết Bóng Ma Mùa Hạ có thiệt hông.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:32.09,0:04:33.30,UNNM_Main_1080p,To,0,0,0,,{Tôi cũng không biết. - Who knows?}Bó tay.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:33.30,0:04:36.30,UNNM_Main_1080p,To,0,0,0,,{\q2}Nhưng mà nghe người ta nói pháo hoa \Ncó thể trấn an linh hồn người chết á.{They do say that fireworks are meant \Nto calm the souls of the dead.}
Dialogue: 100,0:04:38.88,0:04:40.68,UNNM_Main_1080p,Ry,0,0,0,,Họ mà cảm nhận được thì tốt quá.{I hope they see them, then.}
Dialogue: 100,0:04:48.77,0:04:50.10,UNNM_Main_1080p,Ry,0,0,0,,{Không đến rồi. - Looks like it's a no-show.}Công cốc rồi.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:50.65,0:04:52.61,UNNM_Main_1080p,Ao,0,0,0,,{Chúng ta cũng đốt khá nhiều rồi mà. - And we burned through so many, too.}Ừm, đốt quá trời mà hông thấy gì.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:52.94,0:04:54.90,UNNM_Main_1080p,Ry,0,0,0,,{Vậy thì, đây là que cuối rồi. - Okay. Last one.}Thôi đốt cho hết. Que cuối rồi.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:54.90,0:04:55.78,UNNM_Main_1080p,Ry,0,0,0,,Aoi.{Could you, Aoi?}
Dialogue: 100,0:05:04.66,0:05:08.91,UNNM_Main_1080p,Ry,0,0,0,,{[/q2]Tomoya. Tôi, thực ra tin có hồn ma đó. - You know, Tomoya, I actually \Nbelieved we'd get to see it.}Thực lòng mà nói, tôi tin là có ma đó, Tomoya.
Dialogue: 100,0:05:10.08,0:05:11.50,UNNM_Main_1080p,Ry,0,0,0,,{Thật đáng tiếc vì không có. - I'm kinda sad it didn't show up.}{Cơ mà hơi buồn vì vẫn chưa thấy. - OG}Nay chưa thấy nên cũng hơi buồn.
Dialogue: 100,0:05:12.08,0:05:14.67,UNNM_Main_1080p,Ry,0,0,0,,{Nhưng, dạo gần đây là vui nhất đó. - Still, though, I haven't \Nhad this much fun in a while.}Có điều dạo gần đây tôi vui lắm luôn.
Dialogue: 100,0:05:15.67,0:05:17.01,UNNM_Main_1080p,Ry,0,0,0,,{Thật mừng vì đã gặp được hai người. - I'm glad I got to meet you guys.}Có duyên gặp được hai người, mừng lắm.
Dialogue: 100,0:05:17.97,0:05:18.80,UNNM_Main_1080p,Ry,0,0,0,,{Cảm ơn nhé. - Seriously, thank you.}Cảm ơn nha.
Dialogue: 100,0:05:29.48,0:05:31.02,UNNM_Main_1080p,Ry,0,0,0,,Nóng!{Damn, that's hot!}
Dialogue: 100,0:05:31.02,0:05:32.15,UNNM_Main_1080p,Ao,0,0,0,,{Cái gì vậy? - What was that?}Bị cái gì dạ?
Dialogue: 100,0:05:32.15,0:05:33.44,UNNM_Main_1080p,Ao,0,0,0,,{Nghĩa là sao? - Why's it going crazy?}{Hổng hiểu sao tự dưng nó cháy hỗn luôn. - OG}Tự dưng nó phực lên một cái.
Dialogue: 100,0:05:34.69,0:05:35.52,UNNM_Main_1080p,To,0,0,0,,{Đến rồi. - She's real.}Xuất hiện rồi.
Dialogue: 100,0:05:44.49,0:05:46.08,UNNM_Main_1080p,To,0,0,0,,Chị là Bóng Ma Mùa Hạ phải không?{Are you the Summer Ghost?}
Dialogue: 100,0:05:47.20,0:05:48.08,UNNM_Main_1080p,Ay,0,0,0,,{Phải đó. - Indeed.}Phải.
Dialogue: 100,0:05:49.37,0:05:50.79,UNNM_Main_1080p,Ay,0,0,0,check,{Rốt cuộc là có chuyện gì? - To what do I owe the pleasure?}{Mấy người kiếm tôi có việc gì? - OG}Mấy người kiếm tôi có việc gì?
Dialogue: 100,0:05:51.79,0:05:53.21,UNNM_Main_1080p,Ay,0,0,0,check,{Loại người như tôi, - What could you possibly want}Muốn gì mà
Dialogue: 100,0:05:54.17,0:05:55.84,UNNM_Main_1080p,Ay,0,0,0,check,{một người đã chết, - from someone who's already dead?}lại kiếm một người đã chết?
Dialogue: 100,0:06:22.95,0:06:24.07,UNNM_Main_1080p,A,0,0,0,,{\an8}Trúng phóc!{Direct hit!}
Dialogue: 100,0:06:22.95,0:06:24.87,UNNM_Overlap_1080p,B,0,0,0,,{\an8}Thằng này căn chuẩn phết chứ chả đùa.{Your timing's on point, dude.}
Dialogue: 100,0:06:24.07,0:06:24.87,UNNM_Main_1080p,C,0,0,0,,{\an8}Ghê!{Nice one.}
Dialogue: 100,0:06:32.12,0:06:33.87,UNNM_Main_1080p,A,0,0,0,,Làm cái đéo gì vậy con nhỏ này?!{The hell are you doing?!}
Dialogue: 100,0:06:33.87,0:06:34.96,UNNM_Main_1080p,A,0,0,0,,{Đừng có mà giỡn! - Don't be stupid!}Đéo vui đâu!
Dialogue: 100,0:06:34.96,0:06:36.42,UNNM_Main_1080p,A,0,0,0,,Bớt cựa quậy rồi đi xuống giùm!{Quit struggling and get down here!}
Dialogue: 100,0:06:34.96,0:06:36.42,UNNM_Overlap_1080p,Ao,0,0,0,,Thả tui ra!{Let go of me!}
Dialogue: 100,0:06:36.92,0:06:40.26,UNNM_Main_1080p,D,0,0,0,,{\q2}Lâu ngày mới thấy đến trường mà lại đâu vào đó hả?{She finally decides to come to school, \Nand we're back to this already?}
Dialogue: 100,0:06:40.26,0:06:44.05,UNNM_Main_1080p,E,0,0,0,check,Cái kiểu suy nghĩ như vậy, \Nchắc là con bé nó có vấn đề rồi.{If you ask me, the problem's with her.}
Dialogue: 100,0:06:51.22,0:06:55.19,UNNM_Main_1080p,Ao,0,0,0,,{Hồn ma cũng có tầng cấp không ạ? - Do ghosts gang up on each other, too?}Hồn ma có lập bè lập phái\Nđể bắt nạt người khác hông chị?
Dialogue: 100,0:06:56.27,0:06:57.90,UNNM_Main_1080p,Ay,0,0,0,,{Nào, ai biết được. - Hmm, I'm not sure.}Chịu. Đoán xem.
Dialogue: 100,0:06:58.40,0:07:00.40,UNNM_Main_1080p,Ay,0,0,0,,{Cơ bản thì chỉ có mình tôi thôi. - We might be all on our own, actually.}Có khi là thân ai nấy lo thôi.
Dialogue: 100,0:07:02.65,0:07:04.28,UNNM_Main_1080p,Ao,0,0,0,,{Thật mừng quá. - Good.}Vậy thì hay quá.
Dialogue: 100,0:07:04.28,0:07:05.99,UNNM_Main_1080p,Ao,0,0,0,,{Vậy bên kia thoải mái hơn. - I prefer it that way.}Em thích như vậy hơn nhiều.
Dialogue: 100,0:07:05.99,0:07:09.62,UNNM_Main_1080p,Ay,0,0,0,,{Mà, có người thì chắc gì đã tốt. - I get it. Being around people isn't all smiles.}Ừm. Đâu phải cứ có người là toàn niềm vui đâu.
Dialogue: 100,0:07:11.83,0:07:12.62,UNNM_Main_1080p,Ry,0,0,0,,Sao vậy?{What's wrong?}
Dialogue: 100,0:07:13.08,0:07:16.46,UNNM_Main_1080p,To,0,0,0,,Không có gì. Tại để ý thấy pháo hoa cứ cháy suốt.{Nothing. Just noticed \Nthat the sparkler's still going.}
Dialogue: 100,0:07:16.46,0:07:19.17,UNNM_Main_1080p,Ry,0,0,0,,{Thấy khó chịu thật. - You're right. Kinda creepy.}Ừa nhỉ. Thấy ghê ghê sao á.
Dialogue: 100,0:07:20.75,0:07:24.55,UNNM_Main_1080p,Ay,0,0,0,,{Này, em cô đơn ở trong lớp à? - Tell me. Are you an outcast at school?}Em gái bị cô lập trong lớp hả?
Dialogue: 100,0:07:24.55,0:07:26.51,UNNM_Main_1080p,Ay,0,0,0,,{Vì thế nên muốn chết đi phải không? - Is that why you want to die?}Nên mới muốn chết chứ gì?
Dialogue: 100,0:07:27.72,0:07:30.56,UNNM_Main_1080p,Ay,0,0,0,,{Tôi không phải ai cũng thấy đâu. - Thing is, not everyone can see me.}Nói cho mà biết, không phải ai cũng thấy tôi đâu.
Dialogue: 100,0:07:30.56,0:07:32.43,UNNM_Main_1080p,Ay,0,0,0,,{Tôi chỉ thấy được những người - I'm visible only to those}{Người nào thấy được chị - OG}Người nào mà thấy được tôi
Dialogue: 100,0:07:32.43,0:07:34.98,UNNM_Main_1080p,Ay,0,0,0,,{đang sắp sửa chạm vào cái chết mà thôi. - who are within arm's reach of death.}thì sắp chạm vào cửa tử rồi.
Dialogue: 100,0:07:36.56,0:07:39.64,UNNM_Main_1080p,Ao,0,0,0,,Vậy Tomoya với Ryou cũng...{So Tomoya and Ryou also...}
Dialogue: 100,0:07:43.36,0:07:45.07,UNNM_Main_1080p,Ay,0,0,0,,Hai người kia thì sao?{What about you two?}
Dialogue: 100,0:07:45.57,0:07:46.61,UNNM_Main_1080p,Ay,0,0,0,,Hỏi gì không?{Any questions?}
Dialogue: 100,0:07:47.86,0:07:49.20,UNNM_Main_1080p,To,0,0,0,,À thì, chị Bóng Ma Mùa Hạ...{So Summer Ghost, you're—}
Dialogue: 100,0:07:49.20,0:07:50.45,UNNM_Main_1080p,Ay,0,0,0,,Satou Ayane.{Satou Ayane.}
Dialogue: 100,0:07:53.12,0:07:54.71,UNNM_Main_1080p,Ay,0,0,0,,Tên của tôi đó.{I have a name.}
Dialogue: 100,0:07:55.83,0:07:58.13,UNNM_Main_1080p,To,0,0,0,,Chị Ayane là hồn ma phải không?{So Ayane, you're a ghost, right?}
Dialogue: 100,0:07:58.13,0:07:59.96,UNNM_Main_1080p,To,0,0,0,,{Chết đi mọi người đều vậy sao? - Does everyone become one after they die?}Ai chết cũng thành ma à?
Dialogue: 100,0:08:00.34,0:08:01.42,UNNM_Main_1080p,Ay,0,0,0,,Chịu.{Dunno.}
Dialogue: 100,0:08:02.13,0:08:03.71,UNNM_Main_1080p,Ay,0,0,0,,{Câu muốn hỏi gì? - What do you want to know?}Muốn biết gì mà hỏi câu đó?
Dialogue: 100,0:08:04.01,0:08:07.34,UNNM_Main_1080p,To,0,0,0,,{Tôi muốn biết ma nhìn thấy thế giới với đôi mắt nào. - How do ghosts perceive this world?}Em muốn biết ma nhìn thấy thế giới này ra sao.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:07.84,0:08:09.05,UNNM_Main_1080p,To,0,0,0,,{Tôi muốn biết. - I'm curious.}Mong chị trả lời.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:11.05,0:08:12.18,UNNM_Main_1080p,Ay,0,0,0,,{Đó là điều không thể. - I wish I could tell you.}Khó cho tôi rồi.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:13.22,0:08:15.23,UNNM_Main_1080p,Ay,0,0,0,,{Vì không phải cứ giải thích là hiểu được đâu. - It's not something so easily explained.}Vì không phải ngồi nói là hiểu được liền.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:16.48,0:08:19.27,UNNM_Main_1080p,Ay,0,0,0,,{[/q2]Việc của ma thì chỉ có ma mới hiểu. - Some things you can only understand \Nafter you become a ghost.}{Muốn hiểu chuyện của ma thì chỉ có nước làm ma. - OG}Chỉ có làm ma thì mới hiểu chuyện của ma.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:20.19,0:08:21.86,UNNM_Main_1080p,Ay,0,0,0,,{Tôi sắp phải đi rồi. - It's about time I get going.}Sắp sửa tới giờ đi rồi.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:22.44,0:08:23.94,UNNM_Main_1080p,Ay,0,0,0,,{Được nói chuyện với mấy người tôi vui lắm. - It's been fun talking with you.}Nói chuyện với mấy người vui lắm.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:25.03,0:08:25.78,UNNM_Main_1080p,Ay,0,0,0,,{Thôi nhé. - See you.}Chào nha.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:27.20,0:08:28.49,UNNM_Main_1080p,Ay,0,0,0,check,Urameshiya~{Boo.}
Dialogue: 100,0:08:31.07,0:08:33.12,UNNM_Main_1080p,Ao,0,0,0,check,Urameshiya...{B-Boo.}
Dialogue: 100,0:08:35.08,0:08:38.29,UNNM_Main_1080p,Ry,0,0,0,,Không ngờ là lại có ma đó.{So ghosts really do exist, huh?}
Dialogue: 100,0:08:43.71,0:08:44.67,UNNM_Main_1080p,Dc,0,0,0,,Xong rồi.{That'll be all for today.}
Dialogue: 100,0:08:45.26,0:08:47.26,UNNM_Main_1080p,Dc,0,0,0,,Có gì không ổn thì phải liên lạc ngay.{If something happens, \Ncontact me immediately.}
Dialogue: 100,0:08:47.59,0:08:48.80,UNNM_Main_1080p,Ry,0,0,0,,Em hiểu rồi.{I will.}
Dialogue: 100,0:08:49.26,0:08:50.76,UNNM_Main_1080p,Dc,0,0,0,,Phụ huynh em đâu?{Your parents not here today?}
Dialogue: 100,0:08:50.76,0:08:52.43,UNNM_Main_1080p,Ry,0,0,0,,{Họ ở nhà. - I had them stay at home.}Em kêu họ ở nhà rồi.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:52.80,0:08:54.97,UNNM_Main_1080p,Ry,0,0,0,,{Để họ khóc ở bệnh viện thì phiền lắm. - No sense bringing them here just to cry.}Cho họ đi theo rồi khóc lóc ở bệnh viện \Nthì không hay cho lắm.
Dialogue: 100,0:09:01.73,0:09:03.23,UNNM_Main_1080p,Ry,0,0,0,,{Có cố gắng đấy. - You're working hard, huh?}Chăm dữ bây?
Dialogue: 100,0:09:03.94,0:09:05.07,UNNM_Main_1080p,Kh,0,0,0,,Ủa anh?!{Kobayashi!}
Dialogue: 100,0:09:05.07,0:09:06.11,UNNM_Main_1080p,Ry,0,0,0,,Lâu rồi không gặp.{Been a while.}
Dialogue: 100,0:09:08.70,0:09:11.53,UNNM_Main_1080p,Kh,0,0,0,,{Tiền bối, sao anh lại bỏ bóng vậy ạ? - Hey, why did you quit playing?}Cho em hỏi, sao anh nghỉ chơi bóng rổ vậy?
Dialogue: 100,0:09:12.99,0:09:13.95,UNNM_Main_1080p,Ry,0,0,0,,Thích bỏ thôi.{Kinda felt like it.}
Dialogue: 100,0:09:14.20,0:09:15.99,UNNM_Main_1080p,Kh,0,0,0,,Thích bỏ á...{You... felt like it?}
Dialogue: 100,0:09:17.04,0:09:19.16,UNNM_Main_1080p,Ry,0,0,0,,Anh mày sắp chết rồi.{I'm gonna die soon.}
Dialogue: 100,0:09:19.16,0:09:19.62,UNNM_Main_1080p,Kh,0,0,0,,{Hể? - What?}Gì?
Dialogue: 100,0:09:21.67,0:09:23.38,UNNM_Main_1080p,Ry,0,0,0,,{Chỉ còn được 9 tháng nữa. - They're saying I've got nine months left.}Chỉ sống được thêm 9 tháng thôi.
Dialogue: 100,0:09:23.96,0:09:25.80,UNNM_Main_1080p,Ry,0,0,0,,{Không nhìn được hoa anh đào năm sau nữa rồi. - I'll never see the cherry blossoms again.}Khỏi ngắm hoa anh đào năm sau luôn.
Dialogue: 100,0:09:30.01,0:09:31.26,UNNM_Main_1080p,Ry,0,0,0,,{Đùa thôi. - Just kidding.}Giỡn tí.
Dialogue: 100,0:09:32.34,0:09:33.35,UNNM_Main_1080p,Ry,0,0,0,,{Nghĩ thật à? - What, you bought it?}Mày tưởng thiệt à?
Dialogue: 100,0:09:36.77,0:09:39.35,UNNM_Main_1080p,Kh,0,0,0,,{Trời, dừng lại đi. - Oh, come on. Don't scare me like that.}Cái anh này. Đừng có nói chuyện không hên chứ.
Dialogue: 100,0:09:39.35,0:09:41.06,UNNM_Main_1080p,Kh,0,0,0,,Làm em tin sái cổ.{You almost had me worried there.}
Dialogue: 100,0:10:00.66,0:10:01.25,UNNM_Main_1080p,Mo,0,0,0,,Tomoya.{Tomoya.}
Dialogue: 100,0:10:02.00,0:10:03.08,UNNM_Main_1080p,Mo,0,0,0,,{Đến đây một chút đi. - I need to talk to you.}Ra đây nói chuyện xíu.
Dialogue: 100,0:10:04.71,0:10:05.71,UNNM_Main_1080p,Mo,0,0,0,,Tomoya,{Tomoya,}
Dialogue: 100,0:10:05.71,0:10:07.38,UNNM_Main_1080p,Mo,0,0,0,,{con nghe thấy phải không? - I know you can hear me.}con nghe mẹ kêu đúng không?
Dialogue: 100,0:10:07.38,0:10:08.21,UNNM_Main_1080p,To,0,0,0,,{Vâng. - Coming.}Dạ.
Dialogue: 100,0:10:09.80,0:10:13.22,UNNM_Main_1080p,Mo,0,0,0,check,{\q2}Nhìn kết quả từ kỳ thi thử \Ncủa học kỳ một của con đi.{These are your acceptance odds based on \Nyour first trimester mock exams.}
Dialogue: 100,0:10:13.22,0:10:15.14,UNNM_Main_1080p,Mo,0,0,0,check,Toán thì suýt sao .{Your math scores are passable, if barely.}
Dialogue: 100,0:10:15.60,0:10:17.76,UNNM_Main_1080p,Mo,0,0,0,check,{\q2}Vấn đề là bài thi viết trong văn hiện đại.{Your contemporary literature \Nones need work, though.}
Dialogue: 100,0:10:18.27,0:10:20.06,UNNM_Main_1080p,Mo,0,0,0,check,{Không phải viết ra suy nghĩ của bản thân. - You can't just write your own thoughts.}Không phải cứ nghĩ sao viết vậy.
Dialogue: 100,0:10:20.06,0:10:21.73,UNNM_Main_1080p,Mo,0,0,0,check,{Mà viết ra câu trả lời phù hợp với bài thi. - You have to follow the rubric.}Phải trả lời đúng cấu trúc mới có điểm.
Dialogue: 100,0:10:22.60,0:10:24.40,UNNM_Main_1080p,Mo,0,0,0,,{Thực ra là con hiểu mà. - I know you understand that.}Con biết thừa mà đúng không?
Dialogue: 100,0:10:25.02,0:10:26.90,UNNM_Main_1080p,Mo,0,0,0,,{Sao chỉ có phần này là không làm được hả? - Why is it just this one thing?}Có vậy mà cũng không làm được là sao?
Dialogue: 100,0:10:36.55,0:10:38.79,UNNM_Main_1080p,Ao,0,0,0,,Chủ nhật mà cũng đi luyện thi à?{Huh, you go to cram school even on Sundays?}
Dialogue: 100,0:10:39.08,0:10:41.25,UNNM_Main_1080p,To,0,0,0,,{Ừ, vì tôi là thí sinh thi tuyển mà. - Yeah, since I finish high school this year.}Ừ, tại năm nay tôi thi tốt nghiệp mà.
Dialogue: 100,0:10:41.96,0:10:44.54,UNNM_Main_1080p,Ao,0,0,0,,{Hể, tôi là năm sau cơ. - Huh? I've still got a year to go after this.}Ủa? Mình năm sau mới thi lận.
Dialogue: 100,0:10:44.54,0:10:45.67,UNNM_Main_1080p,Ao,0,0,0,,{Tomoya là tiền bối à. - You're older than me, Tomoya?}Vậy Tomoya lớn tuổi hơn hả?
Dialogue: 100,0:10:45.67,0:10:48.46,UNNM_Main_1080p,Ry,0,0,0,,Ủa? Aoi mới lớp 11 hả?{Really? You're only a junior, then?}
Dialogue: 100,0:10:48.46,0:10:50.66,UNNM_Main_1080p,Ao,0,0,0,,{Cả Ryou... nữa à? - What, you're older, too?}Ryou cũng hơn tuổi mình luôn?
Dialogue: 100,0:10:51.72,0:10:53.43,UNNM_Main_1080p,Ry,0,0,0,,{Coi cùng tuổi được rồi. - Yeah, but it doesn't matter. We're friends.}Cứ thoải mái đi. Tuổi tác quan trọng gì.
Dialogue: 100,0:11:16.49,0:11:17.53,UNNM_Main_1080p,Ao/Ry,0,0,0,,{\pos(306,1020)}A lô.{Hello?}
Dialogue: 100,0:11:16.49,0:11:17.53,UNNM_Main_1080p,Ao/Ry,0,0,0,,{\pos(1614,1020)}A lô.{Hello?}
Dialogue: 100,0:11:17.53,0:11:19.66,UNNM_Main_1080p,To,0,0,0,,Sao vậy, Aoi?{What's wrong, Aoi?}
Dialogue: 100,0:11:19.66,0:11:20.79,UNNM_Main_1080p,To,0,0,0,,Có chuyện gì sao?{Did something happen?}
Dialogue: 100,0:11:20.79,0:11:23.87,UNNM_Main_1080p,Ao,0,0,0,,Cũng hông có gì.{No. Not really.}
Dialogue: 100,0:11:23.87,0:11:25.37,UNNM_Main_1080p,Ao,0,0,0,,Chuyện của\N lần trước ấy...{It's just...}
Dialogue: 100,0:11:25.37,0:11:27.92,UNNM_Main_1080p,Ao,0,0,0,,đến bây giờ \Ntôi vẫn chưa tin nổi.{I still can't believe what we saw.}
Dialogue: 100,0:11:27.92,0:11:31.05,UNNM_Main_1080p,Ry,0,0,0,,Mà, không nên \Nnghĩ sâu xa quá làm gì.{Don't let it get to you.}
Dialogue: 100,0:11:31.59,0:11:33.55,UNNM_Main_1080p,Ry,0,0,0,,{Đứa nào mà không sợ mới lạ. - It'd be weird if you weren't spooked.}
Dialogue: 100,0:11:36.09,0:11:36.93,UNNM_Main_1080p,Ry,0,0,0,,Tomoya?{Tomoya?}
Dialogue: 100,0:11:37.47,0:11:38.55,UNNM_Main_1080p,To,0,0,0,,Xin lỗi,{I'm sorry.}
Dialogue: 100,0:11:38.55,0:11:40.60,UNNM_Main_1080p,To,0,0,0,,sắp đến nhà rồi \Nnên tôi cúp máy đây.{I'm almost home, so I'm gonna hang up.}
Dialogue: 100,0:11:40.60,0:11:42.39,UNNM_Main_1080p,To,0,0,0,,Chỉ vậy thôi.{Glad it wasn't anything serious.}
Dialogue: 100,0:11:42.39,0:11:43.35,UNNM_Main_1080p,To,0,0,0,,Chào nhé.{See ya.}
Dialogue: 100,0:11:49.44,0:11:51.61,UNNM_Main_1080p,Ay,0,0,0,,Chào, lâu rồi không gặp.{Heya. Fancy seeing you again.}
Dialogue: 100,0:11:52.65,0:11:56.20,UNNM_Main_1080p,Ay,0,0,0,,{\q2}Vẻ mặt đó, lần trước thôi chưa đủ sao.{Something tells me you \Nweren't satisfied by our last meeting.}
Dialogue: 100,0:11:56.70,0:11:57.95,UNNM_Main_1080p,To,0,0,0,,Một chút thôi.{Not entirely.}
Dialogue: 100,0:12:00.33,0:12:01.58,UNNM_Main_1080p,Ay,0,0,0,,Tham lam vậy.{You just want it all, don't you?}
Dialogue: 100,0:12:04.83,0:12:07.79,UNNM_Main_1080p,Ay,0,0,0,,Này, tại sao Tomoya lại sống?{I'm curious. Why are you alive?}
Dialogue: 100,0:12:09.00,0:12:11.50,UNNM_Main_1080p,To,0,0,0,,Chị thấy em đang sống sao?{Do I look alive to you?}
Dialogue: 100,0:12:11.75,0:12:12.75,UNNM_Main_1080p,Ay,0,0,0,,Ở một mức nào đó.{I'd say so.}
Dialogue: 100,0:12:14.17,0:12:17.55,UNNM_Main_1080p,To,0,0,0,,Em thì không có cái cảm giác đó.{I don't really feel alive, to be honest.}
Dialogue: 100,0:12:18.51,0:12:23.06,UNNM_Main_1080p,To,0,0,0,,Bản thân có đang sống hay không \Nnhiều lúc cũng chả biết nữa.{I sometimes wonder \Nwhether I'm not already dead.}
Dialogue: 100,0:12:24.43,0:12:26.85,UNNM_Main_1080p,Ay,0,0,0,,Trái tim của Tomoya đang chết.{It's because you're dead inside.}
Dialogue: 100,0:12:27.35,0:12:28.19,UNNM_Main_1080p,Ay,0,0,0,,Hại sức khỏe đó.{That's not good for you.}
Dialogue: 100,0:12:28.65,0:12:30.31,UNNM_Main_1080p,To,0,0,0,,Em không muốn bị một con ma nói như vậy.{Don't wanna hear that from a ghost.}
Dialogue: 100,0:12:30.86,0:12:33.11,UNNM_Main_1080p,Ay,0,0,0,,Vậy, rốt cuộc thì cậu muốn sao?{So, what are you going to do about it?}
Dialogue: 100,0:12:35.74,0:12:36.90,UNNM_Main_1080p,To,0,0,0,,Em không biết.{I don't know.}
Dialogue: 100,0:12:38.36,0:12:40.16,UNNM_Main_1080p,To,0,0,0,,Vậy nên em muốn biết.{That's what I was hoping to find out.}
Dialogue: 100,0:12:41.24,0:12:46.54,UNNM_Main_1080p,To,0,0,0,,{\q2}Nếu trở thành ma thì liệu\Nnhững phiền muộn và đau khổ có mất đi không.{Would all my worries, all my suffering, \Nsimply disappear if I became a ghost?}
Dialogue: 100,0:12:47.21,0:12:51.63,UNNM_Main_1080p,To,0,0,0,,{\q2}Nếu hiểu được điều đó, thì có gì sẽ thay đổi cũng nên.{I kind of figured something \Nmight change if I learned that.}
Dialogue: 100,0:12:53.38,0:12:54.42,UNNM_Main_1080p,Ay,0,0,0,,Vậy ư.{I see.}
Dialogue: 100,0:12:56.26,0:12:57.67,UNNM_Main_1080p,Ay,0,0,0,,Muốn thử không?{There's only one way to find out.}
Dialogue: 100,0:13:01.30,0:13:03.76,UNNM_Main_1080p,Ay,0,0,0,,Nào, để đổi gió chút.{Let's get you out of your shell.{WE'RE KEEPING THIS LINE YOU'RE NOT CONVINCING ME OTHERWISE}{NN: Fiiiiiiiiiiiiiiine. You don't have to fight me too hard to keep groaners.}}
Dialogue: 100,0:13:04.10,0:13:05.68,UNNM_Main_1080p,Ay,0,0,0,,Bay cùng tôi nào.{Don't you want to fly?}
Dialogue: 100,0:13:17.07,0:13:17.99,UNNM_Main_1080p,Ay,0,0,0,,Đi thôi.{Let's go!}
Dialogue: 100,0:13:18.90,0:13:21.78,UNNM_Main_1080p,Ay,0,0,0,,Sẵn sàng chưa? Nắm chặt vào.{You ready? Make sure to hold on tight!}
Dialogue: 100,0:13:34.21,0:13:35.38,UNNM_Main_1080p,Ay,0,0,0,,Thế nào?{How is it?}
Dialogue: 100,0:13:35.38,0:13:38.80,UNNM_Main_1080p,Ay,0,0,0,,Cơ thể dưới mặt đất, hồn bay trên trời.{Your body's on the ground. \NBut your soul's flying!}
Dialogue: 100,0:13:38.80,0:13:40.18,UNNM_Main_1080p,Ay,0,0,0,,Cậu đã tự do rồi đó.{You've been freed!}
Dialogue: 100,0:13:43.51,0:13:44.97,UNNM_Main_1080p,To,0,0,0,,Tuyệt thật.{Awesome.}
Dialogue: 100,0:13:47.56,0:13:48.98,UNNM_Main_1080p,To,0,0,0,,Đợi...{W-Wait!}
Dialogue: 100,0:14:12.12,0:14:13.50,UNNM_Main_1080p,To,0,0,0,,{\i1}Trong lòng đất...{I'm inside the ground?}
Dialogue: 100,0:14:15.42,0:14:16.84,UNNM_Main_1080p,Ay,0,0,0,,Thứ lỗi thứ lỗi.{Sorry. I couldn't resist.}
Dialogue: 100,0:14:16.84,0:14:20.05,UNNM_Main_1080p,Ay,0,0,0,,Tôi muốn thấy Tomoya hú hồn một chút.{I wanted to see how you'd react.}
Dialogue: 100,0:14:20.38,0:14:22.09,UNNM_Main_1080p,To,0,0,0,,Chị... có bị ngốc không?{Th-That's just mean.}
Dialogue: 100,0:14:22.34,0:14:23.84,UNNM_Main_1080p,Ay,0,0,0,,Xin lỗi mà.{I said I'm sorry.}
Dialogue: 100,0:14:24.34,0:14:27.47,UNNM_Main_1080p,Ay,0,0,0,,Tôi sẽ dạy cậu cách bay nên hãy tha lỗi đi.{I'll teach you how to fly. \NWill that make up for it?}
Dialogue: 100,0:14:29.64,0:14:30.81,UNNM_Main_1080p,Ay,0,0,0,,Ở nơi sâu thẳm...{Look deep inside you.}
Dialogue: 100,0:14:31.43,0:14:34.48,UNNM_Main_1080p,Ay,0,0,0,,hãy ước trong đáy lòng.{Find the deepest wish in your heart.}
Dialogue: 100,0:14:35.90,0:14:38.23,UNNM_Main_1080p,Ay,0,0,0,,Linh hồn sẽ hướng đến nơi cậu muốn.{Your soul moves where you wish to be.}
Dialogue: 100,0:14:39.07,0:14:41.36,UNNM_Main_1080p,Ay,0,0,0,,Nào, suy nghĩ đi.{Think about it.}
Dialogue: 100,0:14:42.28,0:14:44.11,UNNM_Main_1080p,Ay,0,0,0,,Cậu muốn đi đâu?{Where do you want to go?}
Dialogue: 100,0:14:54.29,0:14:56.21,UNNM_Main_1080p,Ay,0,0,0,,Tomoya thích tranh phải không?{You like paintings, don't you?}
Dialogue: 100,0:14:56.21,0:14:59.88,UNNM_Main_1080p,To,0,0,0,,Vâng, nhưng em đã bỏ rồi.{I do. I quit making them myself, though.}
Dialogue: 100,0:14:59.88,0:15:02.13,UNNM_Main_1080p,To,0,0,0,,Vì có điều quan trọng hơn phải làm.{There's more important things in life, after all.}
Dialogue: 100,0:15:02.97,0:15:04.76,UNNM_Main_1080p,Ay,0,0,0,,Thế nên mới rụt rè vậy sao.{So that's why you seem so dissociated.}
Dialogue: 100,0:15:05.55,0:15:06.97,UNNM_Main_1080p,Ay,0,0,0,,Phí quá.{It's such a waste.}
Dialogue: 100,0:15:06.97,0:15:08.81,UNNM_Main_1080p,Ay,0,0,0,,Mất công đặt chỗ cho rồi.{You're just throwing away this opportunity.}
Dialogue: 100,0:15:09.22,0:15:11.35,UNNM_Main_1080p,Ay,0,0,0,,Bây giờ Tomoya là hồn ma...{You're a ghost right now.}
Dialogue: 100,0:15:11.35,0:15:12.81,UNNM_Main_1080p,Ay,0,0,0,,nên sẽ không có ai giận đâu.{No one can get mad at you, you know.}
Dialogue: 100,0:15:40.30,0:15:42.80,UNNM_Main_1080p,Ay,0,0,0,,Đẹp thật đấy, ánh sáng của đường phố.{Beautiful, huh? All the city lights.}
Dialogue: 100,0:15:43.55,0:15:44.63,UNNM_Main_1080p,To,0,0,0,,Đúng vậy.{You're right.}
Dialogue: 100,0:15:46.38,0:15:49.60,UNNM_Main_1080p,To,0,0,0,,Mà, thực ra thì sẽ sáng hơn đó.{Though it could be brighter, I guess.}
Dialogue: 100,0:15:49.60,0:15:51.31,UNNM_Main_1080p,To,0,0,0,,Vì đèn lúc nào cũng nhấp nháy mà.{Since all the lights aren't on at once.}
Dialogue: 100,0:15:51.31,0:15:54.56,UNNM_Main_1080p,Ay,0,0,0,,{\q2}Này, nói vậy thì gái không theo đâu.{Come on, you're not going to \Nwin over any girls like that.}
Dialogue: 100,0:15:54.56,0:15:56.14,UNNM_Main_1080p,Ay,0,0,0,,Cứ ngoan ngoãn mà biết ơn đi.{Just say thank you like a normal person.}
Dialogue: 100,0:15:56.64,0:15:57.85,UNNM_Main_1080p,To,0,0,0,,Em xin lỗi.{My bad.}
Dialogue: 100,0:16:00.32,0:16:03.07,UNNM_Main_1080p,To,0,0,0,,Cho em hỏi một điều được không?{Hey, may I ask you something?}
Dialogue: 100,0:16:03.53,0:16:04.15,UNNM_Main_1080p,Ay,0,0,0,,Cứ tự nhiên.{Go ahead.}
Dialogue: 100,0:16:05.41,0:16:08.62,UNNM_Main_1080p,To,0,0,0,,Tại sao Ayane lại tự sát vậy ạ?{Why did you commit suicide?}
Dialogue: 100,0:16:11.03,0:16:12.24,UNNM_Main_1080p,Ay,0,0,0,,Tomoya.{Tomoya.}
Dialogue: 100,0:16:14.20,0:16:15.83,UNNM_Main_1080p,Ay,0,0,0,,Cậu đang hiểu lầm đấy.{You've got it wrong.}
Dialogue: 100,0:16:16.71,0:16:18.08,UNNM_Main_1080p,Ay,0,0,0,,Tôi không tự sát.{I didn't commit suicide.}
Dialogue: 100,0:16:19.88,0:16:20.92,UNNM_Main_1080p,Ay,0,0,0,,Muốn biết không?{Are you curious?}
Dialogue: 100,0:16:22.50,0:16:24.05,UNNM_Main_1080p,Ay,0,0,0,,Vậy tôi sẽ nói cho cậu.{I'll tell you my story, then.}
Dialogue: 100,0:16:25.38,0:16:26.34,UNNM_Main_1080p,Ay,0,0,0,,Tôi ấy...{The truth is...}
Dialogue: 100,0:16:28.22,0:16:29.39,UNNM_Main_1080p,Ay,0,0,0,,bị sát hại.{I was killed.}
Dialogue: 100,0:16:32.93,0:16:34.02,UNNM_Main_1080p,To,0,0,0,,Nơi này là...{Where are we?}
Dialogue: 100,0:16:34.02,0:16:35.27,UNNM_Main_1080p,Ay,0,0,0,,Nhà của tôi.{This is my house.}
Dialogue: 100,0:16:35.64,0:16:38.10,UNNM_Main_1080p,Ay,0,0,0,,Bây giờ thì chỉ có mẹ sống một mình thôi.{My mom lives here on her own now.}
Dialogue: 100,0:16:42.27,0:16:45.65,UNNM_Main_1080p,Ay,0,0,0,,3 năm trước, tôi đã cãi nhau với mẹ.{Three years ago, we got into a nasty fight.}
Dialogue: 100,0:16:46.44,0:16:50.16,UNNM_Main_1080p,Ay,0,0,0,,{\q2}Nguyên nhân cuộc cãi vã thực ra chả có gì cả.{Over something so incredibly stupid, too.}
Dialogue: 100,0:16:50.57,0:16:54.24,UNNM_Main_1080p,Ay,0,0,0,,Giữa cơn bão tôi đã lao ra khỏi nhà.{I dashed out of the house \Ninto a horrible typhoon.}
Dialogue: 100,0:16:56.45,0:16:58.50,UNNM_Main_1080p,Ay,0,0,0,,Và thế là khi đi qua đường,{And while I was crossing the street,}
Dialogue: 100,0:16:58.50,0:17:01.58,UNNM_Main_1080p,Ay,0,0,0,,tôi đã bị một xe ô tô vượt đèn đỏ đâm phải.{I was hit by a car that ignored a red light.}
Dialogue: 100,0:17:02.38,0:17:04.00,UNNM_Main_1080p,Ay,0,0,0,,Một câu chuyện vớ vẩn.{It's such a stupid way to die.}
Dialogue: 100,0:17:06.01,0:17:08.84,UNNM_Main_1080p,Ay,0,0,0,,Mà, tôi vẫn còn đang sống.{Except, well, that didn't actually kill me.}
Dialogue: 100,0:17:08.84,0:17:10.76,UNNM_Main_1080p,Ay,0,0,0,,Chỉ bị ngất xỉu thôi.{I was simply unconscious at that point.}
Dialogue: 100,0:17:11.64,0:17:14.97,UNNM_Main_1080p,Ay,0,0,0,,Sau đấy khi mở mắt, \Nthì tôi đã ở trong một nơi chật hẹp.{But when I woke up, \NI was trapped someplace tiny.}
Dialogue: 100,0:17:15.72,0:17:17.85,UNNM_Main_1080p,Ay,0,0,0,,Có lẽ đó là trong một cái vali.{Probably in a suitcase.}
Dialogue: 100,0:17:17.85,0:17:18.94,UNNM_Main_1080p,To,0,0,0,,Tại sao?{But why?}
Dialogue: 100,0:17:18.94,0:17:20.90,UNNM_Main_1080p,Ay,0,0,0,,Để làm cho vụ tai nạn chưa hề xảy ra chứ sao.{To cover up all traces of the accident.}
Dialogue: 100,0:17:21.98,0:17:24.27,UNNM_Main_1080p,Ay,0,0,0,,Tên tài xế đã chôn tôi ở đâu đó.{The driver of that car buried me somewhere.}
Dialogue: 100,0:17:25.19,0:17:29.03,UNNM_Main_1080p,Ay,0,0,0,,{\q2}Tôi cảm thấy khó thở và xa đấy có tiếng tàu vọng lại.{I couldn't breathe, and the only thing \NI could hear was a distant train.}
Dialogue: 100,0:17:30.53,0:17:33.62,UNNM_Main_1080p,Ay,0,0,0,,Đó là ký ức cuối cùng của tôi.{That's my last memory among the living.}
Dialogue: 100,0:17:36.04,0:17:38.41,UNNM_Main_1080p,Ay,0,0,0,,Mẹ đến bây giờ vẫn còn đang đợi tôi.{My mom is still waiting for me to come back.}
Dialogue: 100,0:17:39.12,0:17:40.75,UNNM_Main_1080p,To,0,0,0,,Chị bị chôn ở đâu vậy ạ?{Where were you buried?}
Dialogue: 100,0:17:41.00,0:17:43.25,UNNM_Main_1080p,Ay,0,0,0,,{\q2}Tôi đã định tìm nhưng bỏ cuộc rồi.{I've tried to find that out, \Nbut I've long since given up.}
Dialogue: 100,0:17:43.71,0:17:45.75,UNNM_Main_1080p,Ay,0,0,0,,Bây giờ có làm thì cũng không thay đổi được điều gì.{It's not like it'd change anything at this point.}
Dialogue: 100,0:17:48.46,0:17:51.76,UNNM_Main_1080p,Ay,0,0,0,,Tôi vẫn còn rất nhiều điều muốn làm.{Gosh, there were so many \Nthings I still wanted to do.}
Dialogue: 100,0:17:52.26,0:17:54.22,UNNM_Main_1080p,Ay,0,0,0,,Du lịch hay là yêu đương.{Travel, fall in love...}
Dialogue: 100,0:17:54.72,0:17:57.27,UNNM_Main_1080p,Ay,0,0,0,,Tôi rất ghen tị với người có tương lai xán lạn\N như Tomoya.{I'm jealous of the bright future ahead of you.}
Dialogue: 100,0:17:58.73,0:18:00.98,UNNM_Main_1080p,To,0,0,0,,Du lịch thì làm được mà.{But you can travel, no?}
Dialogue: 100,0:18:00.98,0:18:02.56,UNNM_Main_1080p,To,0,0,0,,Chả mất phí di chuyển.{It wouldn't even cost you anything.}
Dialogue: 100,0:18:02.56,0:18:03.52,UNNM_Main_1080p,Ay,0,0,0,,Ơ kìa,{Careful.}
Dialogue: 100,0:18:03.86,0:18:05.90,UNNM_Main_1080p,Ay,0,0,0,,không tinh tế gì cả.{That was really tactless of you.}
Dialogue: 100,0:18:05.90,0:18:07.61,UNNM_Main_1080p,Ay,0,0,0,,Trừ 20 điểm.{Minus twenty points.}
Dialogue: 100,0:18:09.40,0:18:13.11,UNNM_Main_1080p,To,0,0,0,,Em thì, lại ghen tị với Ayane hơn.{Personally, I think you have it better.}
Dialogue: 100,0:18:15.41,0:18:16.24,UNNM_Main_1080p,Ay,0,0,0,,Tomoya.{Tomoya.}
Dialogue: 100,0:18:16.66,0:18:17.79,UNNM_Main_1080p,To,0,0,0,,Vâng.{Yeah?}
Dialogue: 100,0:18:18.75,0:18:21.50,UNNM_Main_1080p,Ay,0,0,0,,Tôi, muốn đi tìm cơ thể.{I want to find my body.}
Dialogue: 100,0:18:23.08,0:18:25.38,UNNM_Main_1080p,Ay,0,0,0,,Tôi nghĩ nếu có Tomoya thì sẽ làm được.{It might just be possible if you help me.}
Dialogue: 100,0:18:25.92,0:18:30.88,UNNM_Main_1080p,Ay,0,0,0,,{\q2}Lý do mà tôi từ bỏ việc đi tìm là vì dù có tìm thấy \Nđi chăng nữa cũng không sờ vào được.{I only gave up on it because I wouldn't \Nbe able to do anything even if I did.}
Dialogue: 100,0:18:37.97,0:18:39.17,UNNM_Main_1080p,Ay,0,0,0,,Xin lỗi nhé.{Ah, I'm sorry.}
Dialogue: 100,0:18:39.17,0:18:40.98,UNNM_Main_1080p,Ay,0,0,0,,Định đổi gió cho Tomoya một chút mà.{The whole point of this was to cheer you up.}
Dialogue: 100,0:18:41.73,0:18:43.19,UNNM_Main_1080p,Ay,0,0,0,,Chuyện vừa này quên đi nhé.{Pretend I didn't say anything.}
Dialogue: 100,0:18:44.94,0:18:46.19,UNNM_Main_1080p,Ay,0,0,0,,Urameshiya~{Boo.}
Dialogue: 100,0:19:30.19,0:19:32.03,UNNM_Main_1080p,Mo,0,0,0,,Con không đến lò luyện thi sao?{Shouldn't you be in cram school?}
Dialogue: 100,0:19:34.11,0:19:35.11,UNNM_Main_1080p,Mo,0,0,0,,Lên xe đi.{Get in.}
Dialogue: 100,0:19:36.95,0:19:38.45,UNNM_Main_1080p,Mo,0,0,0,,Đã là học kỳ hai rồi đó.{It's already the second trimester.}
Dialogue: 100,0:19:39.16,0:19:41.16,UNNM_Main_1080p,Mo,0,0,0,,Dạo gần đây con lại đi đâu à.{You've been wandering off, haven't you?}
Dialogue: 100,0:19:41.87,0:19:43.33,UNNM_Main_1080p,Mo,0,0,0,,Mẹ biết đó.{You can't lie to me.}
Dialogue: 100,0:19:43.33,0:19:46.29,UNNM_Main_1080p,Ay,0,0,0,,Con đang tìm bạn.{I'm looking for a friend.}
Dialogue: 100,0:19:46.71,0:19:47.88,UNNM_Main_1080p,Mo,0,0,0,,Gì vậy?{Excuse me?}
Dialogue: 100,0:19:47.88,0:19:49.71,UNNM_Main_1080p,Mo,0,0,0,,Việc đó quan trọng hơn tương lai của con sao?{Is that more important than your future?}
Dialogue: 100,0:19:50.75,0:19:53.76,UNNM_Main_1080p,Mo,0,0,0,,{\q2}Từ tuần sau mẹ sẽ đến lò để kiểm tra.{I'll be coming to your cram school \Nto make sure you're there next week.}
Dialogue: 100,0:19:53.76,0:19:55.34,UNNM_Main_1080p,Mo,0,0,0,,Nhìn rõ vào hiện thực đi.{High time you faced reality.}
Dialogue: 100,0:19:56.43,0:19:57.47,UNNM_Main_1080p,Mo,0,0,0,,T-Tomoya?{T-Tomoya!}
Dialogue: 100,0:19:57.89,0:19:58.76,UNNM_Main_1080p,Mo,0,0,0,,Con đang đi đâu vậy?{Where are you going?}
Dialogue: 100,0:20:09.90,0:20:13.19,UNNM_Main_1080p,To,0,0,0,,Hôm nay chúng ta cũng không tìm được nhỉ.{We couldn't find it today either.}
Dialogue: 100,0:20:14.69,0:20:15.53,UNNM_Main_1080p,To,0,0,0,,Xin lỗi chị.{I'm sorry.}
Dialogue: 100,0:20:16.36,0:20:17.41,UNNM_Main_1080p,Ay,0,0,0,,Tại sao?{Why?}
Dialogue: 100,0:20:17.41,0:20:18.66,UNNM_Main_1080p,Ay,0,0,0,,Đừng xin lỗi mà.{There's no need for that.}
Dialogue: 100,0:20:19.24,0:20:21.20,UNNM_Main_1080p,Ay,0,0,0,,Đây cũng như cuộc hẹn hò mà thôi.{Consider this more of a date.}
Dialogue: 100,0:20:23.25,0:20:25.91,UNNM_Main_1080p,To,0,0,0,,Em, năm nay sẽ thi đại học.{I have entrance exams this year.}
Dialogue: 100,0:20:27.50,0:20:32.13,UNNM_Main_1080p,To,0,0,0,,{\q2}Nếu mà học đại học,\Ncó khi em sẽ không thể về thường xuyên được.{Once I start college, I don't know \Nhow much I'll be able to come here.}
Dialogue: 100,0:20:33.67,0:20:34.63,UNNM_Main_1080p,Ay,0,0,0,,Thế à.{I see.}
Dialogue: 100,0:20:36.09,0:20:38.34,UNNM_Main_1080p,Ay,0,0,0,,Vậy, cuộc "Tìm kiếm tôi" đến đây là kết thúc.{Then let's end our \Nsoul-searching journey here.}
Dialogue: 100,0:20:38.34,0:20:38.72,UNNM_Main_1080p,To,0,0,0,,{What?}
Dialogue: 100,0:20:40.34,0:20:42.26,UNNM_Main_1080p,Ay,0,0,0,,Hè cũng đã hết.{Summer is about to end.}
Dialogue: 100,0:20:42.26,0:20:43.85,UNNM_Main_1080p,Ay,0,0,0,,Thời điểm chấm dứt hoàn hảo.{It's a good stopping point.}
Dialogue: 100,0:20:43.85,0:20:45.73,UNNM_Main_1080p,To,0,0,0,,Nhưng, có phải là em muốn bỏ cuộc đâu.{But we don't need to give up comple—}
Dialogue: 100,0:20:45.73,0:20:47.10,UNNM_Main_1080p,Ay,0,0,0,,Thế này là được rồi.{It's fine.}
Dialogue: 100,0:20:47.64,0:20:49.98,UNNM_Main_1080p,Ay,0,0,0,,Nếu cứ tiếp tục thì có lỗi với Tomoya lắm.{I don't want to distract you.}
Dialogue: 100,0:20:49.98,0:20:53.65,UNNM_Main_1080p,Ay,0,0,0,,Đừng có dùng thời gian quý giá của cậu\N cho một người như tôi.{You have more important things to focus on than me.}
Dialogue: 100,0:20:53.65,0:20:54.32,UNNM_Main_1080p,To,0,0,0,,Nhưng mà...{But...}
Dialogue: 100,0:20:54.32,0:20:55.99,UNNM_Main_1080p,Ay,0,0,0,,Trừ hai trăm triệu điểm.{Minus two million points.}
Dialogue: 100,0:20:56.90,0:20:59.28,UNNM_Main_1080p,Ay,0,0,0,,Con trai mà lì lợm thì gái nó không thích đâu.{Being stubborn isn't \Ngoing to win over any girls.}
Dialogue: 100,0:21:00.11,0:21:02.24,UNNM_Main_1080p,Ay,0,0,0,,Tôi đã nói là được rồi.{I said it's fine.}
Dialogue: 100,0:21:02.70,0:21:06.83,UNNM_Main_1080p,To,0,0,0,,{\q2}Thế có nghĩa là Ayane \Nsẽ không còn tồn tại được lâu à?{Does that mean you won't \Nbe around for much longer?}
Dialogue: 100,0:21:07.54,0:21:08.50,UNNM_Main_1080p,Ay,0,0,0,,Có khi vậy.{Possibly.}
Dialogue: 100,0:21:10.17,0:21:11.29,UNNM_Main_1080p,To,0,0,0,,Em đã hiểu rồi.{Okay, then.}
Dialogue: 100,0:21:12.17,0:21:13.59,UNNM_Main_1080p,To,0,0,0,,Gặp lại chị vào lúc chiều tối ngày mai.{I'll see you tomorrow evening.}
Dialogue: 100,0:21:15.13,0:21:16.38,UNNM_Main_1080p,To,0,0,0,,Chị hãy đợi em.{Wait for me, please.}
Dialogue: 100,0:21:19.01,0:21:20.13,UNNM_Main_1080p,To,0,0,0,,Giờ chúng ta có thể gặp không?{Can we meet up?}
Dialogue: 100,0:21:22.14,0:21:23.47,UNNM_Main_1080p,To,0,0,0,,Tôi có chuyện cần bàn.{I wanna talk about something.}
Dialogue: 100,0:21:24.68,0:21:26.39,UNNM_Main_1080p,To,0,0,0,,Tôi muốn đi tìm cơ thể của Ayane.{I want to find Ayane's body.}
Dialogue: 100,0:21:27.06,0:21:28.73,UNNM_Main_1080p,To,0,0,0,,Và tôi muốn hai người giúp.{Will you help me?}
Dialogue: 100,0:21:30.06,0:21:31.77,UNNM_Main_1080p,Ry,0,0,0,,Quả nhiên là chuyện đó à.{I knew it'd be something like that.}
Dialogue: 100,0:21:32.73,0:21:35.36,UNNM_Main_1080p,Ry,0,0,0,,Ông, dạo này hay gặp người ấy nhỉ.{You've been seeing her a lot lately, huh?}
Dialogue: 100,0:21:35.36,0:21:37.09,UNNM_Main_1080p,Ao,0,0,0,,Vậy sao?{What? Really?}
Dialogue: 100,0:21:37.53,0:21:39.11,UNNM_Main_1080p,Ry,0,0,0,,Thích rồi à?{You in love or something?}
Dialogue: 100,0:21:39.82,0:21:40.53,UNNM_Main_1080p,To,0,0,0,,Không phải vậy.{No, that's not it.}
Dialogue: 100,0:21:41.82,0:21:43.03,UNNM_Main_1080p,Ry,0,0,0,,Mà thế nào cũng được.{Well, whatever.}
Dialogue: 100,0:21:43.62,0:21:44.87,UNNM_Main_1080p,Ry,0,0,0,,Vì tôi sẽ không giúp.{I'm not helping, either way.}
Dialogue: 100,0:21:46.08,0:21:48.54,UNNM_Main_1080p,Ry,0,0,0,,{\q2}Tôi không muốn giúp cho người tự sát.{Can't bring myself to help \Nsomeone who killed herself.}
Dialogue: 100,0:21:48.54,0:21:49.62,UNNM_Main_1080p,To,0,0,0,,Không phải.{That's not what happened.}
Dialogue: 100,0:21:49.62,0:21:51.36,UNNM_Main_1080p,To,0,0,0,,Ayane đã bị tai nạn.{She died by no fault of her own.}
Dialogue: 100,0:21:52.58,0:21:54.09,UNNM_Main_1080p,To,0,0,0,,Là một việc quan trọng.{This is really important.}
Dialogue: 100,0:21:54.67,0:21:56.34,UNNM_Main_1080p,To,0,0,0,,Nếu mà không làm{If I don't see this through,}
Dialogue: 100,0:21:57.00,0:21:59.13,UNNM_Main_1080p,To,0,0,0,,thì tôi nghĩ cả đời này sẽ ngồi hối hận.{I think I'll regret it for the rest of my life.}
Dialogue: 100,0:21:59.63,0:22:00.72,UNNM_Main_1080p,Ry,0,0,0,,Vậy à.{That a fact?}
Dialogue: 100,0:22:01.80,0:22:03.22,UNNM_Main_1080p,Ry,0,0,0,,Mong là mọi chuyện sẽ suôn sẻ.{Well, good luck.}
Dialogue: 100,0:22:03.76,0:22:04.22,UNNM_Main_1080p,To,0,0,0,,Ryou.{Ryou—}
Dialogue: 100,0:22:04.22,0:22:05.26,UNNM_Main_1080p,Ry,0,0,0,,Dừng lại đi.{Don't.}
Dialogue: 100,0:22:05.26,0:22:05.51,UNNM_Main_1080p,To,0,0,0,,Đợi đã.{Wait—}
Dialogue: 100,0:22:05.51,0:22:06.76,UNNM_Main_1080p,Ry,0,0,0,,Đã bảo là dừng lại rồi mà.{Seriously, don't!}
Dialogue: 100,0:22:08.64,0:22:09.98,UNNM_Main_1080p,Ry,0,0,0,,Tôi không muốn nghe...{Just drop it.}
Dialogue: 100,0:22:10.48,0:22:11.56,UNNM_Main_1080p,Ry,0,0,0,,những chuyện như vậy{I don't wanna hear it.}
Dialogue: 100,0:22:12.81,0:22:15.90,UNNM_Main_1080p,Ry,0,0,0,,Mấy người thì tốt rồi, có tương lai.{Must be nice having a future.}
Dialogue: 100,0:22:17.36,0:22:18.94,UNNM_Main_1080p,Ry,0,0,0,,Tôi thì không còn nữa.{I don't have that luxury.}
Dialogue: 100,0:22:19.49,0:22:20.82,UNNM_Main_1080p,To,0,0,0,,Thế có nghĩa là...{What does that...}
Dialogue: 100,0:22:21.45,0:22:22.57,UNNM_Main_1080p,Ao,0,0,0,,Ryou.{Ryou!}
Dialogue: 100,0:22:34.08,0:22:36.50,UNNM_Main_1080p,Ay,0,0,0,,Có chuyện gì sao, Tomoya.{Did something happen, Tomoya?}
Dialogue: 100,0:22:36.50,0:22:38.67,UNNM_Main_1080p,To,0,0,0,,Không, không có gì.{Nah. Nothing happened.}
Dialogue: 100,0:22:39.63,0:22:40.42,UNNM_Main_1080p,To,0,0,0,,Cùng tìm nào.{Let's start looking.}
Dialogue: 100,0:22:41.22,0:22:42.38,UNNM_Main_1080p,To,0,0,0,,Trong ngày hôm nay sẽ tìm được.{We'll find your body today.}
Dialogue: 100,0:22:46.85,0:22:47.81,UNNM_Main_1080p,Ao,0,0,0,,Đợi đã.{Wait!}
Dialogue: 100,0:22:48.85,0:22:49.56,UNNM_Main_1080p,Ao,0,0,0,,Ryou.{Ryou!}
Dialogue: 100,0:23:02.53,0:23:03.07,UNNM_Main_1080p,Ao,0,0,0,,Ryou.{Ryou!}
Dialogue: 100,0:23:03.07,0:23:04.07,UNNM_Main_1080p,Ry,0,0,0,,Đừng có đến đây.{Go away!}
Dialogue: 100,0:23:06.37,0:23:07.45,UNNM_Main_1080p,Ry,0,0,0,,Để tôi yên.{Just leave me alone.}
Dialogue: 100,0:23:11.50,0:23:12.66,UNNM_Main_1080p,To,0,0,0,,Chết tiệt.{Damn!}
Dialogue: 100,0:23:14.67,0:23:18.38,UNNM_Main_1080p,Ay,0,0,0,,{\q2}Quả nhiên là Tomoya không thể đi được xa.{It doesn't help that you can't \Ngo too far from your body.}
Dialogue: 100,0:23:18.38,0:23:20.88,UNNM_Main_1080p,To,0,0,0,,Nhưng em nhất định sẽ tìm ra.{Still, I won't stop until we find yours.}
Dialogue: 100,0:23:22.92,0:23:23.97,UNNM_Main_1080p,Ay,0,0,0,,Tomoya.{Tomoya.}
Dialogue: 100,0:23:27.60,0:23:28.80,UNNM_Main_1080p,Ry,0,0,0,,Để cho tôi được yên đi.{Please, leave me alone.}
Dialogue: 100,0:23:31.14,0:23:32.22,UNNM_Main_1080p,Ry,0,0,0,,Mặc dù đã rõ.{I knew it all along.}
Dialogue: 100,0:23:33.64,0:23:35.65,UNNM_Main_1080p,Ry,0,0,0,,Chỉ làm khổ bản thân thêm thôi.{Meeting up with you guys was a mistake.}
Dialogue: 100,0:23:37.77,0:23:40.98,UNNM_Main_1080p,Ry,0,0,0,,{\q2}Nếu đã chết thì một mình tôi đủ rồi,{I would've suffered so much less \Nif I'd just let myself die alone.}
Dialogue: 100,0:23:42.49,0:23:44.32,UNNM_Main_1080p,Ry,0,0,0,,tại sao lại gặp các người chứ.{Why did I do this to myself?}
Dialogue: 100,0:23:46.16,0:23:47.45,UNNM_Main_1080p,Ry,0,0,0,,Tại sao chỉ có tôi...{Why me?}
Dialogue: 100,0:23:49.12,0:23:50.41,UNNM_Main_1080p,Ry,0,0,0,,là mọi chuyện xấu đi chứ.{Why is the world so unfair?}
Dialogue: 100,0:23:51.83,0:23:52.79,UNNM_Main_1080p,Ao,0,0,0,,Ryou.{Ryou.}
Dialogue: 100,0:23:53.87,0:23:58.17,UNNM_Main_1080p,Ao,0,0,0,,{\q2}Tôi không có quyền để nói gì nhưng,\N tôi muốn ông nghe.{I won't try to pretend I understand, \Nbut at least hear me out.}
Dialogue: 100,0:23:59.38,0:24:02.46,UNNM_Main_1080p,Ao,0,0,0,,Tôi nhé, bị bắt nạt ở trường.{I get bullied pretty hard at school.}
Dialogue: 100,0:24:03.42,0:24:05.17,UNNM_Main_1080p,Ao,0,0,0,,Lúc nào cũng đau khổ.{It's put me in some dark places.}
Dialogue: 100,0:24:06.18,0:24:11.68,UNNM_Main_1080p,Ao,0,0,0,,{\q2}Ý nghĩa sống hay gì đó,\N thực sự chả hiểu gì luôn.{I'd begun to lose hope that \NI'd ever understand why I'm even alive.}
Dialogue: 100,0:24:12.93,0:24:18.60,UNNM_Main_1080p,Ao,0,0,0,,{\q2}Vì muốn một câu trả lời mới,\N nên đã tìm đến hồn ma.{To me, searching for a ghost \Nwas a search for new answers.}
Dialogue: 100,0:24:19.56,0:24:22.57,UNNM_Main_1080p,Ao,0,0,0,,{\q2}Có thể khác hoàn toàn với Ryou.{You might be struggling with \Nsomething completely different,}
Dialogue: 100,0:24:22.90,0:24:26.15,UNNM_Main_1080p,Ao,0,0,0,,Nhưng, nhất định Tomoya \Ncũng có điều phiền muộn.{but I'm sure Tomoya's fighting \Na battle of his own, too.}
Dialogue: 100,0:24:27.53,0:24:31.37,UNNM_Main_1080p,Ao,0,0,0,,{\q2}Cuộc gặp mặt của chúng ta \Nnhất định là có ý nghĩa nào đó.{There has to be some meaning \Nin the three of us getting together.}
Dialogue: 100,0:24:35.00,0:24:36.12,UNNM_Main_1080p,To,0,0,0,,Chết rồi.{No way!}
Dialogue: 100,0:24:38.75,0:24:40.21,UNNM_Main_1080p,To,0,0,0,,Ayane.{Ayane.}
Dialogue: 100,0:24:40.21,0:24:41.46,UNNM_Main_1080p,To,0,0,0,,Ayane.{Ayane!}
Dialogue: 100,0:24:41.92,0:24:43.30,UNNM_Main_1080p,To,0,0,0,,Chị có nghe thấy em không?{Can you hear me?}
Dialogue: 100,0:24:47.68,0:24:50.30,UNNM_Main_1080p,Ry,0,0,0,,{\q2}Tomoya mà chuẩn bị hời hợt như vậy sao?{I wouldn't expect you of all people \Nto come so poorly prepared.}
Dialogue: 100,0:24:52.35,0:24:54.68,UNNM_Main_1080p,Ry,0,0,0,,Thực sự có đang tìm kiếm không đấy.{Are you even trying, dude?}
Dialogue: 100,0:24:59.60,0:25:00.52,UNNM_Main_1080p,To,0,0,0,,Xin lỗi.{I'm sorry.}
Dialogue: 100,0:25:01.31,0:25:06.90,UNNM_Main_1080p,To,0,0,0,,{\q2}Tôi chỉ nghĩ cho bản thân, \Ntôi chẳng nghĩ gì cho chuyện của Ryou cả.{I was so focused on myself, \NI didn't consider your situation at all.}
Dialogue: 100,0:25:07.53,0:25:10.11,UNNM_Main_1080p,Ry,0,0,0,,Tôi, rất ghét những loại người như ông.{I hate people like you.}
Dialogue: 100,0:25:11.32,0:25:13.45,UNNM_Main_1080p,Ry,0,0,0,,Cứ ra vẻ là cái gì cũng biết.{You think you've got it all figured out,}
Dialogue: 100,0:25:13.70,0:25:16.37,UNNM_Main_1080p,Ry,0,0,0,,Đã thế còn làm vẻ mặt \Nnhư mình đáng thương nhất vậy.{and yet you look more pitiful than anyone.}
Dialogue: 100,0:25:18.62,0:25:20.12,UNNM_Main_1080p,Ry,0,0,0,,Nhưng tôi sẽ giúp.{But I guess I can help you.}
Dialogue: 100,0:25:21.04,0:25:22.46,UNNM_Main_1080p,Ry,0,0,0,,Hãy cảm ơn Aoi ấy.{You better thank Aoi for this.}
Dialogue: 100,0:25:24.38,0:25:25.21,UNNM_Main_1080p,To,0,0,0,,Ryou.{Ryou.}
Dialogue: 100,0:25:27.42,0:25:28.55,UNNM_Main_1080p,Ry,0,0,0,,Nhanh tiến hành đi.{Let's get this over with.}
Dialogue: 100,0:25:32.47,0:25:33.64,UNNM_Main_1080p,To,0,0,0,,Cảm ơn hai người.{Thank you.}
Dialogue: 100,0:25:58.95,0:26:01.08,UNNM_Main_1080p,Ay,0,0,0,,Liệu sẽ tìm được cơ thể không nhỉ?{You think we'll find it?}
Dialogue: 100,0:26:01.42,0:26:04.21,UNNM_Main_1080p,To,0,0,0,,Sẽ tìm được chứ, với bốn người chúng ta.{Of course. There's four of us now.}
Dialogue: 100,0:26:06.25,0:26:09.13,UNNM_Main_1080p,Ay,0,0,0,,Tôi không nghĩ là các cậu\N lại tìm giúp tôi như thế này.{I didn't think you'd go this far for me.}
Dialogue: 100,0:26:09.84,0:26:11.77,UNNM_Main_1080p,Ay,0,0,0,,Tôi rất biết ơn ba người.{I'm grateful towards all of you.}
Dialogue: 100,0:26:12.59,0:26:14.55,UNNM_Main_1080p,Ay,0,0,0,,Quả nhiên bạn bè là thứ chúng ta luôn nên giữ ở gần.{Nothing beats having friends, huh?}
Dialogue: 100,0:26:15.72,0:26:16.68,UNNM_Main_1080p,Ay,0,0,0,,Phải quý trọng họ đó.{Make sure to cherish them.}
Dialogue: 100,0:26:19.60,0:26:21.02,UNNM_Main_1080p,Ao,0,0,0,,Tomoya.{Tomoya!}
Dialogue: 100,0:26:21.35,0:26:22.73,UNNM_Main_1080p,To,0,0,0,,Aoi. Sao vậy?{Aoi? What's wrong?}
Dialogue: 100,0:26:22.73,0:26:23.70,UNNM_Main_1080p,Ao,0,0,0,,Đến đây nhanh.{Come quickly!}
Dialogue: 100,0:26:24.15,0:26:27.15,UNNM_Main_1080p,Ao,0,0,0,,Có khi chúng tôi đã tìm thấy vali.{I think I might've found the suitcase.}
Dialogue: 100,0:26:32.03,0:26:33.74,UNNM_Main_1080p,Ao,0,0,0,,Ayane, cái đó.{Look there, Ayane.}
Dialogue: 100,0:26:34.20,0:26:35.83,UNNM_Main_1080p,Ay,0,0,0,,Ừ, tôi sẽ lên nhìn.{Thanks. I'll go check it out.}
Dialogue: 100,0:26:38.54,0:26:40.33,UNNM_Main_1080p,Ao,0,0,0,,Ayane sẽ ra sao nhỉ?{I wonder what's gonna happen to her.}
Dialogue: 100,0:26:41.21,0:26:44.92,UNNM_Main_1080p,Ao,0,0,0,,Có khi nào khi tìm thấy cơ thể\N sẽ biến mất luôn không?{Will she disappear once she finds her body?}
Dialogue: 100,0:26:46.13,0:26:47.92,UNNM_Main_1080p,Ao,0,0,0,,Cảm giác cứ buồn buồn kiểu gì ấy.{That's a little sad.}
Dialogue: 100,0:26:51.26,0:26:53.43,UNNM_Main_1080p,Ay,0,0,0,,Chính là nó. Tôi có ở trong đây.{You were right. I'm in there.}
Dialogue: 100,0:26:53.68,0:26:55.76,UNNM_Main_1080p,Ry,0,0,0,,Thật à? Nhanh chóng quay lại mau.{Great! Let's get back.}
Dialogue: 100,0:26:55.76,0:26:56.14,UNNM_Main_1080p,Ao,0,0,0,,{Yeah.}
Dialogue: 100,0:26:57.97,0:26:58.81,UNNM_Main_1080p,Ay,0,0,0,,Mừng quá.{I'm so happy.}
Dialogue: 100,0:26:59.93,0:27:02.49,UNNM_Main_1080p,Ay,0,0,0,,Giờ thì mẹ có thể thoải mái được rồi.{Hopefully my mom can rest easy now.}
Dialogue: 100,0:27:03.19,0:27:05.98,UNNM_Main_1080p,To,0,0,0,,Quả nhiên là, Ayane sẽ biến mất sao?{So you are gonna disappear.}
Dialogue: 100,0:27:06.69,0:27:07.90,UNNM_Main_1080p,Ay,0,0,0,,Có khi vậy.{I'd expect so.}
Dialogue: 100,0:27:08.65,0:27:10.65,UNNM_Main_1080p,Ay,0,0,0,,Nhưng tôi vui lắm.{But I had a lot of fun.}
Dialogue: 100,0:27:10.65,0:27:12.82,UNNM_Main_1080p,Ay,0,0,0,,Cuối cùng đã cho tôi những ký ức đẹp.{I made the most of my remaining time here.}
Dialogue: 100,0:27:17.03,0:27:17.78,UNNM_Main_1080p,Ay,0,0,0,,Tomoya.{Tomoya.}
Dialogue: 100,0:27:19.24,0:27:20.46,UNNM_Main_1080p,Ay,0,0,0,,Cố gắng lên.{Hang in there.}
Dialogue: 100,0:27:24.00,0:27:27.38,UNNM_Main_1080p,Ay,0,0,0,,Cậu liệu mà sống cho tử tế đó.{You have to keep on living.}
Dialogue: 100,0:27:29.38,0:27:31.38,UNNM_Main_1080p,Ry,0,0,0,,Dậy rồi này.{Look. He's finally awake.}
Dialogue: 100,0:27:31.63,0:27:33.30,UNNM_Main_1080p,Ry,0,0,0,,Sao cứ ngẩn người ra thế, đi nào.{What are you spacing out for?}
Dialogue: 100,0:27:33.30,0:27:33.92,UNNM_Main_1080p,Ry,0,0,0,,Tôi lo lắm đấy.{Let's go!}
Dialogue: 100,0:27:33.92,0:27:35.26,UNNM_Main_1080p,To,0,0,0,,Ờ, ừ.{Sure.}
Dialogue: 100,0:27:35.55,0:27:37.05,UNNM_Main_1080p,Ay,0,0,0,,Tôi lo lắm đấy.{I'm a little worried.}
Dialogue: 100,0:27:37.05,0:27:39.47,UNNM_Main_1080p,Ay,0,0,0,,Làm hồn ma cũng chẳng có gì vui lắm đâu.{You had so much fun while you were a ghost.}
Dialogue: 100,0:27:40.26,0:27:46.02,UNNM_Main_1080p,Ay,0,0,0,,{\q2}Đừng có nghĩ là chết đi chút thôi\N cũng không tệ lắm đâu nhá.{I hope you haven't started thinking \Ndeath might not be so bad.}
Dialogue: 100,0:27:47.77,0:27:48.98,UNNM_Main_1080p,Ay,0,0,0,,Thiệt tình mà.{My, oh my.}
Dialogue: 100,0:27:52.48,0:27:55.10,UNNM_Main_1080p,Ay,0,0,0,,Xin lỗi nhé vì cái tính ích kỷ này.{I'm sorry for dragging you into this.}
Dialogue: 100,0:27:59.28,0:27:59.70,UNNM_Main_1080p,To,0,0,0,,Ryou.{Ryou!}
Dialogue: 100,0:27:59.70,0:28:01.29,UNNM_Main_1080p,Ry,0,0,0,,Kệ tôi, cứ đi trước đi.{I'm fine. Go on without me.}
Dialogue: 100,0:28:02.12,0:28:03.87,UNNM_Main_1080p,Ry,0,0,0,,Đừng để Ayane chờ lâu quá.{Don't make Ayane wait.}
Dialogue: 100,0:28:11.50,0:28:12.50,UNNM_Main_1080p,To,0,0,0,,Là nơi này.{It's gotta be here.}
Dialogue: 100,0:28:12.50,0:28:13.34,UNNM_Main_1080p,Ao,0,0,0,,{Yeah.}
Dialogue: 100,0:28:13.80,0:28:15.01,UNNM_Main_1080p,Ao,0,0,0,,Nhưng mà cái này.{But how do we get over?}
Dialogue: 100,0:28:15.84,0:28:19.72,UNNM_Main_1080p,Ay,0,0,0,,{\q2}Tomoya đã lo lắng như vậy,\N tôi thì lại tự ý dẫn cậu đi lung tung.{You're going through your own thing, \Nand I selfishly dragged you into mine.}
Dialogue: 100,0:28:21.18,0:28:21.89,UNNM_Main_1080p,Ay,0,0,0,,Kết cục,{And after all that,}
Dialogue: 100,0:28:23.10,0:28:25.18,UNNM_Main_1080p,Ay,0,0,0,,tôi lại để cậu lại đi mất.{I'm going to move on without you.}
Dialogue: 100,0:28:26.60,0:28:28.27,UNNM_Main_1080p,Ay,0,0,0,,Đừng có mà buồn ấy nhá.{Don't miss me, please.}
Dialogue: 100,0:28:28.27,0:28:29.15,UNNM_Main_1080p,To,0,0,0,,Em...{I...}
Dialogue: 100,0:28:30.31,0:28:31.94,UNNM_Main_1080p,To,0,0,0,,muốn tìm thấy Ayane.{I want to find you, Ayane.}
Dialogue: 100,0:28:32.57,0:28:33.73,UNNM_Main_1080p,To,0,0,0,,Bây giờ thì chỉ thế thôi.{That's all that matters right now.}
Dialogue: 100,0:28:37.40,0:28:38.28,UNNM_Main_1080p,Ay,0,0,0,,Hiểu rồi.{Okay.}
Dialogue: 100,0:28:41.53,0:28:43.62,UNNM_Main_1080p,Ay,0,0,0,,Chắc chắn là cậu cũng đã hiểu rõ rồi nhỉ.{I'm sure that'll give you your answer.}
Dialogue: 100,0:28:44.45,0:28:48.83,UNNM_Main_1080p,Ay,0,0,0,,{\q2}Là quá khứ của tôi, với cậu là tương lai.{For you, death is in the future; \Nfor me, it's in the past.}
Dialogue: 100,0:28:49.92,0:28:52.00,UNNM_Main_1080p,Ay,0,0,0,,Nó ngăn cách giữa chúng ta.{It's wedged right between us.}
Dialogue: 100,0:29:01.43,0:29:02.26,UNNM_Main_1080p,To,0,0,0,,Aoi?{Aoi?}
Dialogue: 100,0:29:02.26,0:29:05.27,UNNM_Main_1080p,Ao,0,0,0,,Còn lại thì nhờ vào cậu đó, Tomoya.{You take it from here, Tomoya!}
Dialogue: 100,0:29:30.33,0:29:30.75,UNNM_Main_1080p,Ay,0,0,0,,Đi thôi.{Let's go.}
Dialogue: 100,0:29:31.96,0:29:34.38,UNNM_Main_1080p,Ao,0,0,0,,Sao vậy, Tomoya?{What's wrong, Tomoya?}
Dialogue: 100,0:29:34.75,0:29:35.71,UNNM_Main_1080p,Ao,0,0,0,,Tomoya.{Tomoya!}
Dialogue: 100,0:29:40.68,0:29:43.64,UNNM_Main_1080p,Ay,0,0,0,,Vì cậu đã ở trong trạng thái linh hồn\N suốt một thời gian dài,{You spent a lot of time \Ndetached from your body.}
Dialogue: 100,0:29:44.14,0:29:45.76,UNNM_Main_1080p,Ay,0,0,0,,nên mới tới đây.{That's why you're here right now.}
Dialogue: 100,0:29:47.89,0:29:49.06,UNNM_Main_1080p,Ay,0,0,0,,Đây là cái chết.{This place is death.}
Dialogue: 100,0:29:49.94,0:29:51.06,UNNM_Main_1080p,Ay,0,0,0,,Không có gì cả.{There's nothing here.}
Dialogue: 100,0:29:51.60,0:29:54.23,UNNM_Main_1080p,Ay,0,0,0,,Nhưng lại là chỗ tập hợp tất cả những thứ của cậu.{But it's also where all of your self is.}
Dialogue: 100,0:29:57.74,0:29:59.89,UNNM_Main_1080p,Ay,0,0,0,,Nếu mà đốt thứ này thì tất cả đều kết thúc.{Once you burn this, it's all over.}
Dialogue: 100,0:30:00.45,0:30:02.78,UNNM_Main_1080p,Ay,0,0,0,,Và rồi có thể chào tạm biệt thực tại.{You'll part with the real world.}
Dialogue: 100,0:30:09.08,0:30:11.67,UNNM_Main_1080p,Ay,0,0,0,,Quả nhiên là không tốt nhỉ.{Yeah. I guess we shouldn't do this.}
Dialogue: 100,0:30:13.17,0:30:15.00,UNNM_Main_1080p,Ay,0,0,0,,Tại sao khuôn mặt cậu lại như vậy?{Why do you look so sad?}
Dialogue: 100,0:30:17.34,0:30:20.34,UNNM_Main_1080p,Ay,0,0,0,,Thực ra là cậu muốn thế nào?{What do you truly want?}
Dialogue: 100,0:30:33.81,0:30:35.15,UNNM_Main_1080p,Ry,0,0,0,,Tomoya!{Tomoya!}
Dialogue: 100,0:30:36.32,0:30:38.32,UNNM_Main_1080p,Ry,0,0,0,,Làm gì vậy cha, mở mắt ra!{The hell are you doing?! Wake up!}
Dialogue: 100,0:30:38.32,0:30:38.98,UNNM_Main_1080p,Ao,0,0,0,,Ryou.{Ryou?}
Dialogue: 100,0:30:38.98,0:30:41.03,UNNM_Main_1080p,Ry,0,0,0,,Là chuyện do ông quyết cơ mà.{You wanted to do this more than anyone.}
Dialogue: 100,0:30:41.03,0:30:43.28,UNNM_Main_1080p,Ry,0,0,0,,Cố mà làm đến cùng đi.{So see it through the end!}
Dialogue: 100,0:30:43.28,0:30:45.70,UNNM_Main_1080p,Ry,0,0,0,,Đừng có bỏ cuộc ở nơi này.{Why would you give up now?}
Dialogue: 100,0:30:46.53,0:30:48.49,UNNM_Main_1080p,Ry,0,0,0,,Tôi không tha cho đâu.{Like hell I'm gonna let you!}
Dialogue: 100,0:30:49.45,0:30:52.62,UNNM_Main_1080p,To,0,0,0,,Không được, em phải quay về.{No. I have to go back.}
Dialogue: 100,0:30:52.62,0:30:53.67,UNNM_Main_1080p,Ay,0,0,0,,Tại sao?{Why?}
Dialogue: 100,0:30:57.75,0:30:59.38,UNNM_Main_1080p,Ay,0,0,0,,Có ý nghĩa gì chứ.{What's the point?}
Dialogue: 100,0:31:00.05,0:31:03.80,UNNM_Main_1080p,Ay,0,0,0,,{\q2}Sao cứ phải bám lấy \Ncái thế giới khắc nghiệt đến như vậy?{Why would you cling onto a world \Nthat only makes you suffer?}
Dialogue: 100,0:31:08.68,0:31:09.31,UNNM_Main_1080p,Ay,0,0,0,,Tại sao?{Why?!}
Dialogue: 100,0:31:15.15,0:31:18.77,UNNM_Main_1080p,To,0,0,0,,Đúng là toàn những điều mà em chán ghét.{You're right. My life's nothing but a chore.}
Dialogue: 100,0:31:20.03,0:31:21.44,UNNM_Main_1080p,To,0,0,0,,Nhưng vẫn chưa kết thúc.{But it's not over yet!}
Dialogue: 100,0:31:22.57,0:31:25.28,UNNM_Main_1080p,To,0,0,0,,Với Kyou và Aoi.{Just like Ryou and Aoi,}
Dialogue: 100,0:31:25.78,0:31:29.95,UNNM_Main_1080p,To,0,0,0,,{\q2}Chỉ cần ngẩng mặt lên một chút\Nlà có thể có những cuộc gặp gỡ mới lạ.{I learned that if you just look up, \Nthere's always someone waiting to pick you up.}
Dialogue: 100,0:31:31.20,0:31:33.33,UNNM_Main_1080p,To,0,0,0,,Ngươi không phải là Ayane.{You're not Ayane.}
Dialogue: 100,0:31:33.33,0:31:35.29,UNNM_Main_1080p,To,0,0,0,,{\q2}Chính là tôi đang đi tìm lý do để chết.{You're the part of me that's \Nlooking for a reason to die!}
Dialogue: 100,0:31:36.21,0:31:40.42,UNNM_Main_1080p,To,0,0,0,,Tôi phải trở lại với thực tại, và đi tìm Ayane.{I need to get back to \Nthe real world and find Ayane.}
Dialogue: 100,0:31:41.09,0:31:42.80,UNNM_Main_1080p,To,0,0,0,,Với tôi thì sẽ là một ngày nào đó,{My time's going to come one day.}
Dialogue: 100,0:31:43.67,0:31:46.01,UNNM_Main_1080p,To,0,0,0,,Với Ayane thì đã qua rồi.{Ayane's time has already passed.}
Dialogue: 100,0:31:46.72,0:31:47.68,UNNM_Main_1080p,To,0,0,0,,Tôi...{I've...}
Dialogue: 100,0:31:48.30,0:31:50.60,UNNM_Main_1080p,To,0,0,0,,Tôi phải chấp nhận những điều đó trước đã!{I've gotta come to terms with those things first!}
Dialogue: 100,0:32:13.45,0:32:13.95,UNNM_Main_1080p,Ao,0,0,0,,Tomoya.{Tomoya!}
Dialogue: 100,0:32:13.95,0:32:14.37,UNNM_Main_1080p,Ry,0,0,0,,Tomoya.{Tomoya!}
Dialogue: 100,0:32:45.74,0:32:46.78,UNNM_Main_1080p,To,0,0,0,,Tốt quá rồi.{I'm so glad.}
Dialogue: 100,0:33:00.00,0:33:02.88,UNNM_Main_1080p,Ay,0,0,0,,Cảm ơn cậu vì đã tìm thấy tôi.{Thank you for finding me.}
Dialogue: 100,0:33:19.39,0:33:20.60,UNNM_Main_1080p,Mo,0,0,0,,Vâng.{Coming.}
Dialogue: 100,0:33:33.58,0:33:34.49,UNNM_Main_1080p,Mo,0,0,0,,Ayane?{Ayane?}
Dialogue: 100,0:34:17.66,0:34:20.50,UNNM_Main_1080p,To,0,0,0,,Mùa hè, lại đến rồi nhỉ.{So, summer's come again, huh?}
Dialogue: 100,0:34:24.63,0:34:27.42,UNNM_Main_1080p,Ry,0,0,0,,Này, sau đấy hai người thế nào?{How have you guys been doing?}
Dialogue: 100,0:34:28.05,0:34:29.46,UNNM_Main_1080p,Ry,0,0,0,,Có đang sống khỏe mạnh không đấy?{Things looking up at all?}
Dialogue: 100,0:34:32.13,0:34:32.93,UNNM_Main_1080p,To,0,0,0,,Ừm.{Yeah.}
Dialogue: 100,0:34:34.93,0:34:36.05,UNNM_Main_1080p,To,0,0,0,,Bằng một cách nào đó.{Somewhat.}
Dialogue: 100,0:34:40.68,0:34:44.56,UNNM_Main_1080p,To,0,0,0,,{\q2}Sống cho bản thân thực ra khó hơn tôi nghĩ.{Living for yourself isn't the walk \Nin the park I thought it would be.}
Dialogue: 100,0:34:45.44,0:34:46.19,UNNM_Main_1080p,Ao,0,0,0,,Tôi nữa.{Same here.}
Dialogue: 100,0:34:48.94,0:34:51.53,UNNM_Main_1080p,Ao,0,0,0,,Vẫn còn tệ ơi là tệ.{Of course my life isn't suddenly all roses, but...}
Dialogue: 100,0:34:56.83,0:35:00.70,UNNM_Main_1080p,Ao,0,0,0,,Đừng... có lúc nào cũng đối xử với tôi như trẻ con nữa.{H-How long are you gonna \Nbehave like children?!}
Dialogue: 100,0:35:00.70,0:35:02.83,UNNM_Main_1080p,Ao,0,0,0,,Nhưng dần dần cũng thay đổi đi từng chút.{But I feel like I'm taking small steps, at least.}
Dialogue: 100,0:35:05.33,0:35:10.21,UNNM_Main_1080p,To,0,0,0,,Có lẽ nào cứ làm như ta được bảo sẽ dễ dàng hơn.{Maybe it'd be easier \Nif I just did what I was told.}
Dialogue: 100,0:35:11.34,0:35:12.84,UNNM_Main_1080p,To,0,0,0,,Đôi khi tôi cũng suy nghĩ.{I do doubt myself sometimes.}
Dialogue: 100,0:35:14.55,0:35:15.43,UNNM_Main_1080p,To,0,0,0,,Nhưng mà kệ đi.{But it's fine.}
Dialogue: 100,0:35:16.55,0:35:20.60,UNNM_Main_1080p,To,0,0,0,,Dù có chuyện gì.{All things eventually come to an end.}
Dialogue: 100,0:35:20.89,0:35:23.10,UNNM_Main_1080p,To,0,0,0,,Đằng nào cũng sẽ kết thúc, \Nthì không có gì phải sợ nữa.{Whenever I think that, all my fear disappears.}
Dialogue: 100,0:35:25.35,0:35:28.86,UNNM_Main_1080p,To,0,0,0,,Tôi sẽ lựa chọn bản thân mình để tiến bước.{I'll be the one to make \Nthe decisions for myself.}
Dialogue: 100,0:35:34.36,0:35:35.45,UNNM_Main_1080p,Ry,0,0,0,,Tốt quá.{Good for you.}
Dialogue: 100,0:35:41.58,0:35:42.87,UNNM_Main_1080p,Ry,0,0,0,,Sắp hết giờ rồi.{We're running out of time.}
Dialogue: 100,0:35:43.83,0:35:45.67,UNNM_Main_1080p,Ry,0,0,0,,Thật mừng vì được nói chuyện với hai người.{I'm glad I got to talk to you guys.}
Dialogue: 100,0:35:46.42,0:35:48.38,UNNM_Main_1080p,Ry,0,0,0,,Vì lúc cuối không có cơ hội.{Since I didn't get to say goodbye.}
Dialogue: 100,0:35:52.76,0:35:54.63,UNNM_Main_1080p,Ry,0,0,0,,Tại sao mình lại được sinh ra chứ?{Why was I even born?}
Dialogue: 100,0:35:55.38,0:35:57.34,UNNM_Main_1080p,Ry,0,0,0,,Tôi đã suy nghĩ về chuyện đó suốt.{That's the only thought \Nthat crossed my mind.}
Dialogue: 100,0:35:59.10,0:36:05.02,UNNM_Main_1080p,Ry,0,0,0,,{\q2}Nhưng, tôi tin là mình sẽ khỏi, \Nvà đã sống được đến mùa xuân.{But I got to see the next spring \Nbecause I believed I could be cured.}
Dialogue: 100,0:36:06.90,0:36:10.69,UNNM_Main_1080p,Ry,0,0,0,,{\q2}Đừng có làm vẻ mặt đó \Nvới cái thằng đã chết nửa năm trước.{Stop crying over someone \Nwho's been dead for months.}
Dialogue: 100,0:36:11.73,0:36:14.99,UNNM_Main_1080p,Ry,0,0,0,,Nếu là hai người thì việc gì cũng sẽ qua thôi.{I'm sure things will work out for both of you.}
Dialogue: 100,0:36:15.78,0:36:19.12,UNNM_Main_1080p,Ry,0,0,0,,Không có bảo đảm, nhưng để tôi bảo kê cho.{I don't have any proof of that, \Nbut I guarantee you they will.}
Dialogue: 100,0:36:20.28,0:36:21.04,UNNM_Main_1080p,Ry,0,0,0,,Tomoya.{Tomoya.}
Dialogue: 100,0:36:22.29,0:36:23.12,UNNM_Main_1080p,Ry,0,0,0,,Aoi.{Aoi.}
Dialogue: 100,0:36:24.91,0:36:26.21,UNNM_Main_1080p,Ry,0,0,0,,Cố gắng mà sống cho tốt nhá.{Live your best lives.}
Dialogue: 100,0:36:49.02,0:36:50.12,UNNM_Main_1080p,Ao,0,0,0,,Về thôi.{Let's head back.}
Dialogue: 100,0:36:53.36,0:36:54.18,UNNM_Main_1080p,To,0,0,0,,Ừ.{Sure.}
